ng%20if%20your%20partner's%20actions%20align%20with%20their%20words.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20constantly%20giving%20the%20same%20feedback%20and%20asking%20for%20the%20same%20thing%20or%20a%20similar%20thing%20in%20different%20presentations%2C%20and%20it%20all%20boils%20down%20to%2C%20'Show%20me%20that%20you're%20committed%20to%20me%2C%20show%20me%20that%20you%20prioritize%20me%2C%20show%20me%20that%20I%20matter'%20%E2%80%94%20don't%20be%20afraid%20to%20be%20critical%20of%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Bejar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20said%20people%20must%20be%20willing%20to%20walk%20away%20from%20a%20partner%20when%20they%20don't%20meet%20their%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20huge%20sticking%20point%20for%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20Bejar%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20not%20prepared%20to%20say%2C%20'I'm%20not%20going%20to%20try%20to%20change%20you%20anymore.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWithout%20that%2C%20then%20you'll%20tolerate%20whatever%2C%20or%20you'll%20keep%20complaining%2C%20and%20either%20you'll%20be%20upset%20all%20the%20time%2C%20or%20you%20might%20get%20something%20like%20a%20shut-up%20ring%20that%20just%20alleviates%20the%20complaining%20in%20the%20short%20term%20but%20doesn't%20lead%20to%20what%20you%20actually%20want%2C%20which%20is%20the%20marriage%2C%26quot%3B%20Bejar%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20ring%20is%20just%20an%20object.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBejar%20said%20if%20your%20values%20and%20hopes%20for%20your%20relationship%20aren't%20aligned%2C%20the%20engagement%20won't%20mean%20much%20in%20the%20long%20run%3A%20%26quot%3BYou're%20going%20to%20get%20a%20ring%2C%20not%20a%20marriage.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b3c11a34-9812-4b1a-9635-26e07d329b38%5C%22%3EHappily%20ever%20after%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMillington%20hopes%20sharing%20her%20experience%20on%20social%20media%20can%20help%20other%20people%20avoid%20shut-up%20rings%20and%20unhappy%20relationships.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp