must%20step%20out%20only%20after%20informing%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAvoid%20going%20off-campus%20during%20late%20or%20odd%20hours.%20All%20Hostel%20borders%20should%20abide%20by%20the%20hostel%20norms%20%26amp%3B%20regulations%20laid%20by%20the%20institute%20and%20administration.%20Be%20cautious%20and%20avoid%20associating%20with%20individuals%20who%20appear%20unknown%20or%20are%20suspicious%20in%20nature%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20advisory%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20added%20that%20women%20doctors%20and%20students%20must%20always%20ensure%20they%20have%20a%20means%20of%20making%20emergency%20contact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20on%20duty%20you%20should%20be%20well%20composed%20emotionally%2C%20remain%20alert%20about%20the%20surroundings%20and%20should%20graciously%20interact%20with%20the%20public%2C%20so%20that%20you%20don't%20attract%20unnecessary%20attention%20of%20unscrupulous%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20advisory%20added%20in%20another%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20document%20said%20students%20and%20women%20doctors%20must%20immediately%20communicate%20any%20grievances%20to%20internal%20committees%20to%20address%20harassment%20or%20ragging.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20advisory%20said%20it%20had%20been%20issued%20in%20the%20greater%20interest%20of%20doctors%2C%20students%20and%20staff%20members%20of%20the%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20advisory%20drew%20sharp%20criticism%20on%20campus%2C%20with%20the%20students%20saying%20that%20authorities%20should%20improve%20security%20arrangements%20instead%20of%20telling%20them%20to%20stay%20in%20their%20rooms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssam%20Chief%20Minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20said%20that%20the%20advisory%20was%20%26quot%3Bnot%20warranted%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20he%20had%20spoken%20to%20the%20principal%20of%20the%20medical%20college.%20%26quot%3BThat%20advisory%20has%20been%20withdrawn%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Junior%20Doctors'%20Association%20of%20the%20college%20condemned%20the%20advisory%20and%20said%20the%20language%20in%20the%20document%20is%20disturbing.%20They%20demanded%20adequate%20lighting%20on%20campus%2C%20security%20measures%20in%20doctors'%20room%20and%20more%20CCTV%20cameras.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESalman%20Chaudhury%2C%20president%20of%20the%20junior%20doctors'%20association%2C%20said%20they%20have%20given%20the%20authorities%2048%20hours%20to%20fulfill%20their%20demands.%20%26quot%3BThe%20circular%20is%20deeply%20regressive%2C%20misogynistic%20to%20some%20extent%20and%20very%20outrageous%20for%20all%20female%20doctors%20working%20here.%20The%20authorities%20must%20revoke%20this%20circular%20and%20fulfill%20our%20demands%2C%20failing%20which%20we%20would%20be%20forced%20to%20start%20a%20protest%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESocial%20media%20users%20too%20criticised%20the%20advisory%20and%20said%20it%20asks%20women%20to%20%26quot%3Bbehave%26quot%3B%20and%20implicitly%20holds%20them%20responsible%20for%20acts%20of%20sexual%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20user%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20advisory%20should%20be%20for%20the%20men%20and%20not%20women%26quot%3B.%20Another%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3BCan%20any%20female%20doctor%20feel%20safe%20even%20at%20their%20own%20workplace%20reading%20such%20notices%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723627860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fd5ar6j8o_silchar-medical-college_625x300_14_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkolkata-doctor-rape-murder-rg-kar-medical-college-avoid-being-alone-assam-hospitals-advisory-after-kolkata-rape-murder-6333986%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Days%20after%20a%2031-year-old%20doctor%20was%20raped%20and%20murdered%20at%20Kolkata's%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%2C%20a%20state-run%20medical%20college%20in%20Assam%20has%20issued%20an%20advisory%20for%20women%20doctors%20and%20students%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22en