dnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Foyo-q1-result-firm-posts-1st-ever-profit-of-rs-229-cr-eyes-expansion-124081400994_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Foyo-q1-result-firm-posts-1st-ever-profit-of-rs-229-cr-eyes-expansion-124081400994_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20next%20big%20status%20symbol%20in%20real%20estate%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Luxury%20products%20amid%20a%20city%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66bb6f865da406397bf55d15%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ETimo%20Lenzen%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Italian%20carmaker%20Pagani%20produces%20fewer%20than%20100%20vehicles%20a%20year%2C%20and%20each%20comes%20with%20a%20seven-figure%20price%20tag.%20The%20brand%20is%20known%20among%20gearheads%20for%20its%20attention%20to%20detail%20and%20air%20of%20exclusivity%2C%20qualities%20that%20Pagani%20hopes%20will%20translate%20to%20its%20next%20project%3A%20luxury%20condominiums.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20spring%2C%20the%20company%20unveiled%20plans%20for%20Pagani%20Residences%2C%20a%2070-unit%20condo%20development%20in%20Miami's%20North%20Bay%20Village.%20The%20automaker%20says%20the%20building%20will%20offer%20waterfront%20views%20and%20living%20spaces%20%26quot%3Bmeticulously%20curated%26quot%3B%20by%20its%20interior-design%20arm.%20Pagani%20condos%2C%20much%20like%20Pagani%20cars%2C%20start%20at%20about%20%243%20million.%20But%20for%20people%20desperate%20to%20claim%20a%20piece%20of%20Pagani%2C%20the%20price%20tag%20may%20be%20no%20problem%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20sold%20a%20unit%20to%20a%20guy%20that%20loves%20Pagani%20cars%2C%20and%20it%20just%20didn't%20matter%20to%20him%20what%20the%20location%20was%2C%26quot%3B%20Carlo%20Dipasquale%2C%20a%20luxury-real-estate%20agent%20in%20South%20Florida%2C%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BThey%20could've%20built%20the%20building%20inland%2C%20anywhere%20in%20Miami%2C%20for%20all%20he%20cared.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPagani%20is%20the%20latest%20high-end%20car%20brand%20to%20lend%20its%20name%20to%20a%20shiny%20condo%20project%20along%20the%20Miami%20coast%2C%20joining%20the%20likes%20of%20Mercedes-Benz%2C%20Porsche%2C%20Aston%20Martin%2C%20and%20Bentley.%20Beyond%20automakers%2C%20there's%20a%20growing%20list%20of%20luxury%20brands%20hoping%20to%20use%20real%20estate%20to%20turn%20their%20cultural%20cachet%20into%20cold%2C%20hard%20cash.%20The%20owner%20of%20the%20trendy%20Italian%20eatery%20Carbone%20is%20partnering%20with%20developers%20on%20a%20high-rise%3B%20Dolce%20%26amp%3B%20Gabbana%20also%20has%20one%20in%20the%20works.%20Even%20Elle%20magazine%20announced%20this%20spring%20that%20it%20would%20get%20in%20on%20the%20action%20with%20a%20condo%20project%20near%20Miami%20Beach%2C%20hoping%20to%20sell%20buyers%20on%20a%20lifestyle%20pulled%20straight%20from%20its%20glossy%20pages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20heard%20of%20these%20plans%20a%20few%20months%20ago%2C%20I%20was%20tempted%20to%20dismiss%20them%20as%20the%20kinds%20of%20vanity%20projects%20that%20matter%20only%20to%20people%20with%20too%20much%20money%20and%20an%20insatiable%20hunger%20for%20status.%20Some%20of%20the%20announcements%20also%20struck%20me%20as%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20stretch.%20Magazines%20have%20a%20hard%20enough%20time%20peddling%20subscriptions%20these%20days%20%E2%80%94%20what%20makes%20them%20so%20sure%20they%20can%20sell%20condos%3F%20But%20as%20I%20talked%20with%20more%20people%2C%20it%20became%20clear%20that%20so-called%20branded%20residences%20are%20a%20global%20phenomenon%20that's%20here%20to%20stay%2C%20with%20developers%20laying%20the%20groundwork%20for%20branded%20towers%20in%20hot%20spots%20like%20Dubai%2C%20London%2C%20and%20New%20York.%20The%20hottest%20%E2%80%94%20and%20weirdest%20%E2%80%94%20trend%20in%20condominiums%20could%20actually%20tell%20us%20a%20lot%20about%20the%20future%20of%20real%20estate%2C%20not%20to%20mention%20our%20brand-addled%20brains.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20concept%20of%20branded%20real-estate%20projects%20isn't%20new.%20New%20York's%20five-star%20Sherry-Netherland%20Hotel%20began%20welcoming%20long-term%20residents%20almost%20a%20century%20ago%2C%20and%20since%20then%20roughly%20700%20branded%20residences%20have%20graced%20skylines%20around%20the%20world.%20But%20the%20recent%20boom%20in%20these%20projects%20makes%20it%20clear%20that%20we've%20entered%20a%20new%20era%3A%20More%20than%20650%20branded%20projects%20are%20set%20to%20open%20over%20the%20next%20five%20years%2C%20a%20doubling%20that%20Riyan%20Itani%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20the%20specialty%20consulting%20firm%20Global%20Branded%20Residences%2C%20told%20me%20is%20%26quot%3Bpretty%20much%20unprecedented%20in%20any%20sector.%26quot%3B%20Condo%20developers%20these%20days%20are%20laser-focused%20on%20the%20bottom%20line%2C%20and%20they%20believe%20linking%20up%20with%20a%20well-known%20label%20will%20help%20them%20sell%20units%20faster%20and%20at%20higher%20prices.%20Brands%20like%20Elle%20or%20Pagani%20stand%20to%20collect%20some%20nice%20licensing%20fees%2C%20too.%20But%20that's%20not%20what%20they're%20really%20after.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20about%20outreach%20to%20a%20customer%20base%20beyond%20your%20core%20business%2C%26quot%3B%20Itani%20said.%20Whether%20you%20sell%20handbags%20or%20golf%20clubs%2C%20%26quot%3Byou're%20able%20to%20reach%20out%20in%20a%20different%20way%20and%20get%20brand%20loyalty.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20digital%20rendering%20of%20a%20Pagani%20car%20parked%20outside%20the%20planned%20Pagani%20Residences%20condo%20development%20at%20sunset.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66ba6050b4912df3ae1ae5e5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221754%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20rendering%20of%20the%20planned%20Pagani%20Residences%20in%20Miami%2C%20starting%20at%20%243%20million%20per%20unit.%3Cp%3EWe%20Are%20Visuals%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20these%20projects%20are%20tied%20to%20big%2C%20swanky%20hospitality%20names%20like%20Four%20Seasons%20or%20Ritz-Carlton%2C%20which%20set%20aside%20parts%20of%20their%20buildings%20as%20for-sale%20units.%20These%20arrangements%20feel%20like%20natural%20unions%20%E2%80%94%20if%20you're%20a%20big-money%20traveler%20with%20a%20fierce%20loyalty%20to%20the%20Four%20Seasons%2C%20for%20example%2C%20you%20might%20be%20inclined%20to%20purchase%20a%20home%20that%20promises%20the%20same%20level%20of%20comfort%2C%20service%2C%20and%20brand%20recognition.%20But%20a%20smaller%20slice%20of%20branded%20residences%2C%20about%2020%25%2C%20are%20partnerships%20between%20forward-thinking%20real-estate%20developers%20and%20companies%20that%20appear%20to%20have%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20housing.%20These%20are%20the%20most%20attention-grabbing%2C%20and%20sometimes%20head-scratching%2C%20marriages%3A%20Lamborghini%20villas%20in%20Dubai%20and%20Spain%3B%20Nobu%20Residences%20in%20Toronto%2C%20named%20for%20the%20Japanese%20Peruvian%20restaurant%20favored%20by%20celebrities%20like%20Drake%3B%20a%20Miami%20tower%20branded%20by%20the%20fine%20crystal%20maker%20Baccarat%20that%20touts%20the%20tagline%20%26quot%3BWhere%20life%20forever%20sparkles.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20as%20if%20these%20luxury-goods%20companies%20suddenly%20morphed%20into%20real-estate%20experts.%20They%20typically%20license%20their%20names%20to%20seasoned%20development%20firms%20that%20front%20the%20money%20for%20these%20projects%2C%20shepherd%20them%20to%20the%20finish%20line%2C%20and%20ultimately%20bear%20the%20risk%20and%20reward%20of%20the%20actual%20condo%20sales.%20While%20the%20brands%20leave%20the%20number%20crunching%20and%20floor%20planning%20to%20the%20developers%2C%20they%20weigh%20in%20on%20design%20flourishes%20%E2%80%94%20Giorgio%20Armani%20himself%20apparently%20lends%20a%20personal%20touch%20to%20the%20interiors%20of%20Residences%20by%20Armani%20Casa%20in%20South%20Florida%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20condos'%20marketing%20campaigns.%20The%20contributions%20may%20appear%20comparatively%20small%2C%20but%20adding%20a%20well-known%20company%20to%20the%20marquee%20can%20deliver%20real%20results%20for%20the%20building's%20owner.%20Itani%20estimates%20that%20developers%20working%20on%20a%20branded%20residence%20spend%20an%20extra%2010%25%20to%2015%25%20of%20what%20they%20would%20spend%20on%20a%20standard%20condo%20project%2C%20since%20they%20have%20to%20pay%20for%20all%20the%20additional%20amenities%20and%20the%20right%20to%20splash%20the%20brand's%20logo%20across%20the%20building.%20But%20in%20crowded%20cities%20like%20New%20York%20or%20Miami%2C%20a%20recognizable%20logo%20can%20help%20a%20new%20building%20stand%20out.%20It%20also%20translates%20to%20cash%3A%20Itani%20told%20me%20units%20in%20branded%20towers%20go%20for%20a%20global%20average%20of%2030%25%20more%20than%20comparable%20non-branded%20units.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20kind%20of%20a%20no-brainer%20for%20a%20developer%2C%26quot%3B%20Itani%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BFrom%20a%20financial%20standpoint%2C%20it's%20a%20very%20profitable%20enterprise.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3ENo-brainers%20for%20developers%20aren't%20always%20a%20win%20for%20consumers%20(take%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20the%20recent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-are-new-homes-ugly-construction-builders-design-materials-architecture-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erace%20toward%20the%20bottom%20in%20homebuilding%3C%2Fa%3E).%20But%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20branded%20residences%2C%20there%20are%20real%20selling%20points%20for%20buyers.%20Brand%20loyalists%20may%20be%20eager%20to%20welcome%20their%20favorite%20company%20into%20yet%20another%20corner%20of%20their%20lives.%20They're%20invited%20to%20consider%20what%20it%20might%20feel%20like%20to%20%3Cem%3Elive%20%3C%2Fem%3Einside%20a%20Lambo%20rather%20than%20merely%20speed%20down%20the%20coastal%20highway%20in%20one.%20There's%20a%20novelty%20aspect%20to%20these%20purchases%2C%20too.%20Plenty%20of%20people%20own%20luxury%20condos%2C%20but%20far%20fewer%20get%20to%20flex%20a%20prestigious%20name%20like%20Bentley%20or%20Porsche%20when%20directing%20visitors%20to%20their%20new%20pad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDevelopers%20load%20up%20these%20buildings%20with%20amenities%20to%20help%20discerning%20buyers%20feel%20like%20they're%20getting%20bang%20for%20their%20buck.%20Convenience%20waits%20around%20every%20corner%3A%20infinity%20pools%20and%20thermal%20spas%2C%20private%20boat%20slips%2C%20rooftop%20helipads.%20The%20Bentley%20Residences%20allows%20owners%20to%20park%20their%20cars%20in%20their%20units%20via%20a%20vehicle%20elevator.%20Villa%20Miami%2C%20the%2058-story%20Miami%20condo%20project%20from%20Major%20Food%20Group%2C%20which%20owns%20a%20slew%20of%20exclusive%20restaurants%20such%20as%20the%20impossible-to-get-a-table-at%20Carbone%2C%20promises%20residents%20private%20dining%20experiences%20and%20VIP%20status%20at%20all%20its%20outposts.%20Hotels%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20offer%20to%20list%20branded%20condos%20on%20Airbnb%20and%20manage%20them%20when%20their%20owners%20aren't%20there%2C%20helping%20buyers%20make%20a%20return%20on%20investment%20even%20in%20their%20absence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20attraction%20of%20these%20glitzy%20homes%2C%20however%2C%20may%20be%20peace%20of%20mind.%20Plenty%20of%20condos%20are%20vying%20for%20rich%20buyers'%20eyes%20and%20wallets%2C%20and%20they're%20not%20all%20created%20equal.%20But%20when%20a%20prestigious%20name%20like%20Aston%20Martin%20or%20Dolce%20%26amp%3B%20Gabbana%20stakes%20its%20reputation%20on%20a%20project%2C%20buyers%20get%20some%20added%20assurance%20that%20the%20units%20will%20meet%20%E2%80%94%20or%20exceed%20%E2%80%94%20their%20lofty%20standards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20are%20all%20very%20well-known%2C%20established%20brands%20that%20people%20feel%20comfortable%20buying%20into%2C%26quot%3B%20Laura%20Steinbruckner%2C%20a%20luxury%20agent%20in%20the%20Miami%20area%2C%20told%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDevelopers%20aren't%20likely%20to%20stray%20too%20far%20from%20this%20lucrative%20pitch.%20Luxury%20brands%20will%20probably%20always%20offer%20the%20biggest%20upside%20for%20builders%2C%20and%20even%20the%20%26quot%3Bnon-luxury%26quot%3B%20projects%20in%20the%20pipeline%20are%20still%20tied%20to%20respected%20brands%20like%20Hilton%20and%20are%20only%20slightly%20cheaper%20than%20the%20big-name%20buildings.%20But%20developers%20interested%20in%20branded%20residences%20have%20a%20plethora%20of%20other%20candidates%2C%20some%20of%20which%20could%20stretch%20the%20boundaries%20of%20the%20sector%20even%20further.%20The%20Elle%20project%20may%20seem%20out%20of%20left%20field%2C%20but%20Itani%20told%20me%20he's%20talking%20with%20another%20publication%20interested%20in%20making%20similar%20inroads.%20After%20all%2C%20magazines%20like%20Elle%20portray%20enviable%20lifestyles%20tied%20to%20fashion%2C%20celebrity%2C%20health%2C%20and%20beauty.%20All%20those%20things%20could%20translate%20to%20experiences%20within%20buildings%2C%20Itani%20told%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20not%20to%20say%20all%20branded%20residences%20offer%20the%20same%20gilded%20path%20to%20profits.%20Car%20companies%20and%20fashion%20labels%2C%20unlike%20hotels%2C%20aren't%20known%20for%20their%20property-management%20chops%2C%20and%20there's%20a%20risk%20that%20buyers%20eventually%20tire%20of%20the%20marketing%20schtick.%20In%20a%20few%20years%2C%20you%20may%20well%20see%20some%20condo%20owners%20complaining%20that%20they%20got%20a%20Fiat%20level%20of%20service%20when%20they%20were%20promised%20a%20Ferrari.%20Rob%20Sykes%2C%20an%20associate%20principal%20at%20the%20global%20design%20firm%20WATG%20who%20advises%20companies%20on%20hotels%20and%20branded%20residences%2C%20told%20me%20developers%20shouldn't%20count%20on%20slapping%20a%20big%20name%20on%20a%20building%20and%20instantly%20reaping%20rewards.%20But%20he%20does%20expect%20to%20see%20the%20sector%20expand%20as%20non-hotel%20brands%20enter%20the%20market%20%E2%80%94%20just%20last%20year%20he%20was%20in%20conversations%20with%20a%20client%20who%20was%20interested%20in%20bringing%20a%20luxury%20jewelry%20brand%20(he%20wouldn't%20name%20names)%20into%20the%20fray.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EItani%20was%20still%20amazed%20that%20two%20sectors%20in%20particular%20%E2%80%94%20tech%20and%20food%20%E2%80%94%20hadn't%20made%20more%20of%20a%20splash%20in%20the%20world%20of%20branded%20residences.%20There%20are%20a%20few%20big%20restaurant%20names%2C%20including%20Nobu%2C%20Major%20Food%20Group%2C%20and%20Cipriani%2C%20the%20famed%20Italian%20eatery.%20But%20Itani%20envisions%20a%20world%20in%20which%20many%20other%20newcomers%20turn%20corner-table%20regulars%20into%20corner-unit%20owners.%20He%20also%20sees%20an%20opening%20for%20ubiquitous%20tech%20companies%20like%20Apple%20or%20Google%20to%20sell%20loyal%20fans%20yet%20another%20product%2C%20one%20tricked%20out%20with%20all%20the%20latest%20tech%20and%20infused%20with%20their%20design%20ethos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20there%20are%20two%20things%20that%20a%20modern%20human%20being%20cares%20most%20about%2C%20it's%20what%20they're%20putting%20in%20their%20mouth%20and%20what%20phone%20they've%20got%20in%20their%20pocket%2C%26quot%3B%20Itani%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BSo%20I%20would%20expect%20to%20see%20those%20two%20elements%20represented.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Fjames-rodriguez%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3EJames%20Rodriguez%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20reporter%20on%20Business%20Insider's%20Discourse%20team.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fluxury-real-estate-condos-miami-branded-residences-porsche-lamborghini-homebuyers-2024-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723627441000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66bb6fc1955b01c3294e0c4e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fluxury-real-estate-condos-miami-branded-residences-porsche-lamborghini-homebuyers-2024-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Luxury%20brands%20like%20Porsche%20and%20Nobu%20are%20splashing%20their%20names%20across%20condo%20buildings%20as%20part%20of%20real%20estate's%20hottest%20%E2%80%94%20and%20weirdest%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0new%20trend.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jrodriguez%40insider.com%20(James%20Rodriguez)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fluxury-real-estate-condos-miami-branded-residences-porsche-lamborghini-homebuyers-2024-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Amid%20Cognizant's%202.5%20LPA%20freshers%20pay%20offer%20row%2C%20attention%20on%20CEO's%20salary%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723627161000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-05%2F27%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F400X400%2F1716779070-4773.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Famid-cognizant-s-2-5-lpa-freshers-pay-offer-row-attention-on-ceo-s-salary-124081400970_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20the%20uproar%20over%20the%20low%20entry-level%20salary%2C%20attention%20has%20turned%20to%20Cognizant's%20CEO%2C%20who%20is%20the%20highest-paid%20in%20India%20with%20Ravi%20Kumar%20Singisetti%20receiving%20a%20staggering%20%2422.56%20million%20last%20year%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22can