20to%20police%2C%20the%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20intervened%20and%20ordered%20that%20the%20case%20be%20transferred%20to%20the%20central%20agency%20at%20once.%20This%20was%20a%20rare%20occasion%20when%20a%20court%20ordered%20transfer%20of%20the%20case%20during%20the%20first%20hearing%20in%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20led%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20TS%20Sivagnanam%20noted%20that%20there%20has%20been%20%26quot%3Bno%20significant%20progress%20in%20the%20investigation%26quot%3B%20so%20far%20and%20flagged%20the%20possibility%20of%20destruction%20of%20evidence.%20The%20court%20also%20noted%20serious%20lapses%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20hospital%20administration%20and%20slammed%20the%20former%20Principal%2C%20whose%20resignation%20and%20swift%20reinstatement%20in%20a%20key%20role%20has%20sparked%20a%20row.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20some%20of%20the%20key%20points%20the%20high%20court%20made%20in%20its%20order%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Petitions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMultiple%20public%20interest%20litigations%20were%20filed%20in%20the%20high%20court%20with%20the%20common%20prayer%20that%20state%20police%20hand%20over%20the%20investigation%20to%20CBI%20or%20any%20other%20independent%20agency.%20Among%20the%20petitioners%20were%20the%20victim's%20parents%20and%20BJP%20leader%20Suvendu%20Adhikari.%20The%20court's%20order%20noted%20that%20the%20petitioners%20had%20said%20there%20were%20injuries%20on%20the%20victim's%20body%20and%20that%20Chief%20Minister%20Banerjee%20had%20said%20the%20state%20government%20has%20no%20objection%20if%20the%20probe%20was%20transferred%20to%20CBI.%20The%20parents%2C%20sought%20a%20probe%20monitored%20by%20the%20high%20court%20to%20ensure%20that%20no%20evidence%20is%20tampered%20with%20or%20destroyed.%20The%20parents%20also%20sought%20protection%20for%20themselves%2C%20witnesses%20and%20any%20other%20individual%20who%20may%20have%20information%20related%20to%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3