6quot%3B.%20At%2010.53%20am%20the%20next%20day%2C%20the%20parents%20said%2C%20the%20Assistant%20Superintendent%20of%20the%20hospital%20informed%20them%20that%20their%20daughter%20was%20unwell.%20About%2022%20minutes%20later%2C%20the%20same%20Assistant%20Superintendent%20told%20them%20that%20their%20daughter%20had%20committed%20suicide%20on%20hospital%20premises.%20%26quot%3BThe%20petitioners%20immediately%20rushed%20to%20the%20hospital%20and%20according%20to%20them%2C%20they%20were%20not%20permitted%20to%20see%20their%20daughter's%20body%20and%20they%20were%20made%20to%20wait%20for%203%20hours%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20order%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20petitions%20%26quot%3Bsuspect%20that%20this%20delay%20was%20intentional%26quot%3B.%20The%20victim's%20parents%20said%20that%20they%20were%20allowed%20to%20see%20the%20body%20only%20after%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20intervened.%20By%20this%20time%2C%20a%20large-scale%20agitation%20had%20started%20on%20the%20campus%20of%20the%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20petitioners%20have%20narrated%20the%20state%20in%20which%20the%20body%20of%20their%20daughter%20was%20found%20when%20they%20were%20permitted%20to%20see%20and%20they%20would%20state%20that%20there%20were%20bleeding%20injuries%20over%20the%20body%20and%20there%20were%20no%20cloth%20on%20the%20lower%20part%20of%20the%20body%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20order%20says%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20parents%20suspect%20that%20more%20than%20one%20individual%20were%20offenders%20and%20their%20suspicion%20is%20that%20it%20is%20a%20case%20of%20gang%20rape%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Bengal%20Government%20Said%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20government's%20counsel%20said%20that%20the%20police%20outpost%20at%20the%20medical%20college%20and%20hospital%20received%20information%20about%20the%20incident%20at%2010.10%20am%20Friday.%20%26quot%3BAt%2010%3A30%20a.m.%20the%20local%20police%20viz.%20Tala%20Police%20Station%20was%20informed.%20At%2011%3A00%20a.m.%20homicidal%20team%20reached%20the%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%20and%20by%20then%20more%20than%20150%20people%20had%20gathered.%20It%20is%20submitted%20that%20at%2011%3A30%20a.m.%2C%20the%20Additional%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%20and%20senior%20officers%20were%20at%20site.%20The%20parents%20of%20the%20victim%20arrived%20at%201%3A00%20pm%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20state%20counsel%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20government%20said%20that%20it%20is%20false%20that%20the%20parents%20were%20made%20to%20wait%20for%20three%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20government%20said%20the%20body%20of%20the%20victim%20could%20not%20be%20moved%20out%20of%20the%20seminar%20hall%20because%20of%20the%20agitation%20and%20a%20doctor%20examined%20the%20body%20in%20the%20seminar%20hall.%20Later%2C%20the%20Rapid%20Action%20Force%20had%20to%20be%20called%20in%20and%20the%20post-mortem%20was%20done%20between%206.10%20pm%20and%207.10%20pm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F1hts0t78_sandip-ghosh-rg-kar-principal_625x300_12_August_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECourt%20Raps%20Principal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20came%20down%20heavily%20on%20the%20Dr%20Sandip%20Ghosh%2C%20the%20former%20Principal%20of%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20who%20has%20made%20headlines%20for%20his%20resignation%20and%20swift%20reinstatement%20as%20Principal%20of%20another%20medical%20college.%20%26quot%3BThe%20court%20said%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Bdisheartening%26quot%3B%20that%20the%20Principal%20was%20not%20%26quot%3Bpro-active%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Principal%20of%20the%20institution%20either%20by%20himself%20or%20by%20issuing%20appropriate%20directions%20could%20have%20lodged%20a%20complaint%20with%20the%20police%20since%20the%20death%20occurred%20within%20the%20hospital%20premises.%20This%2C%20in%20our%20view%2C%20was%20a%20clear%20dereliction%20of%20duty%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20Principal%20and%20the%20officers%20under%20his%20command%20and%20this%20has%20led%20to%20various%20repercussions%20and%20it%20has%20been%20admitted%20by%20the%20authorities%20that%20the%20situation%20became%20chaotic%20and%20Rapid%20Action%20Force%20had%20to%20be%20brought%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBengal%20Pulled%20Up%20For%20Reinstating%20Principal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20flagged%20that%20Dr%20Ghosh%20was%20made%20Principal%20of%20National%20Medical%20College%20%26amp%3B%20Hospital%20%26quot%3Bwithin%20the%20shortest%20possible%20time%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20difficult%20to%20comprehend%20as%20to%20why%20when%20a%20person%20submits%20his%20resignation%2C%20the%20concerned%20authority%20of%20the%20State%20did%20not%20exercise%20the%20two%20options%2C%20which%20are%20available%20i.e.%20either%20to%20accept%20the%20resignation%20or%20to%20refuse%20to%20accept%20the%20resignation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20said%20the%20state%20authority%20should%20bear%20in%20mind%20the%20circumstances%20that%20led%20to%20the%20resignation.%20%26quot%3BTherefore%2C%20even%20assuming%20the%20resignation%20was%20not%20accepted%2C%20the%20least%20that%20can%20be%20expected%20from%20a%20responsible%20higher%20official%20of%20the%20concerned%20department%20is%20to%20immediately%20relieve%20the%20Principal%20from%20his%20duties%20and%20not%20assign%20him%20any%20other%20duty%20of%20equal%20responsibility.%20If%20this%20course%20had%20not%20been%20adopted%20and%20if%20he%20has%20been%20assigned%20another%20responsibility%20equivalent%20to%20the%20responsibility%20held%20by%20them%2C%20it%20would%20tantamount%20to%20putting%20a%20premium%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20order%20says%20questioning%20the%20%26quot%3Btearing%20urgency%26quot%3B%20in%20giving%20Dr%20Ghosh%20a%20new%20role.%20The%20court%20asked%20Dr%20Ghosh%20to%20go%20on%20leave%20immediately%20and%20said%20he%20shall%20not%20be%20permitted%20to%20hold%20the%20post%20of%20Principal%20of%20National%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%2C%20Calcutta%20until%20further%20directions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Why%20Case%20Of%20Unnatural%20Death'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20shredded%20the%20hospital%20administration%20over%20unnatural%20death%20case%20registered%20after%20the%20doctor%20was%20found%20dead.%20Saying%20that%20his%20was%20%26quot%3Bquite%20disturbing%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20court%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20deceased%20victim%20was%20a%20doctor%20working%20in%20the%20hospital%2C%20it%20is%20rather%20surprising%20as%20to%20why%20the%20Principal%2Fhospital%20did%20not%20lodge%20a%20formal%20complaint.%20This%2C%20in%20our%20view%2C%20was%20a%20serious%20lapse%2C%20giving%20room%20for%20suspicion.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20government's%20counsel%20submitted%20that%20the%20unnatural%20death%20case%20was%20registered%20since%20there%20was%20no%20complaint%20at%20that%20point%20of%20time%20from%20any%20corner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20noted%20that%20the%20crime%20spot%20assumes%20extraordinary%20importance%20because%20it%20is%20a%20government%20hospital%20and%20the%20victim%20was%20a%20doctor%20working%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BConsidering%20these%20factors%2C%20we%20would%20be%20well-justified%20in%20making%20an%20observation%20that%20the%20administration%20was%20not%20with%20the%20victim%20or%20the%20family%20of%20the%20victim%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BA%20Peculiar%20Case%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20noted%20that%20%26quot%3Bunder%20normal%20circumstances%26quot%3B%2C%20it%20could%20have%20asked%20for%20a%20report%20from%20the%20investigators.%20%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20the%20case%20on%20hand%2C%20is%20a%20peculiar%20case%20and%20the%20facts%20and%20circumstances%20warrant%20appropriate%20orders%20without%20further%20loss%20of%20time.%20We%20are%20convinced%20to%20say%20so%20because%20even%20after%20a%20lapse%20of%20five%20days%20there%20appears%20to%20be%20no%20significant%20progress%20in%20the%20investigation%2C%20which%20ought%20to%20have%20happened%20by%20now%20and%20by%20further%20loss%20of%20time%2C%20we%20would%20be%20well-justified%20in%20accepting%20the%20plea%20raised%20by%20the%20writ%20petitioners%2C%20more%20particularly%2C%20the%20parents%20of%20the%20victim%20that%20there%20is%20every%20possibility%20that%20the%20evidence%20will%20be%20destroyed%20and%20the%20witnesses%20will%20be%20influenced%20etc%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20order%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F3pfu0klg_kolkata-protest_625x300_13_August_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFeatureCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20'Public%20Confidence'%20Angle%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20point%20the%20court%20stressed%20on%20its%20order%20is%20the%20need%20to%20instill%20confidence%20among%20public%20that%20the%20horrific%20incident%20is%20being%20properly%20investigated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20pointed%20out%20by%20the%20Hon'ble%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20one%20of%20the%20circumstances%2C%20which%20the%20Court%20should%20take%20note%20while%20transferring%20an%20investigation%20from%20the%20State%20Investigating%20Agency%20to%20any%20other%20independent%20agency%20is%20to%20do%20justice%20between%20the%20parties%20and%20to%20instill%20confidence%20in%20the%20public%20mind.%20Apart%20fro