20Bajrang%20Punia%2C%20and%20Sakshi%20Malik%20protested%20for%20about%20a%20year%20over%20the%20allegations%20made%20against%20former%20wrestling%20body%20chief%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20look%20at%20it%20from%20the%20other%20angle%2C%20the%20protests%20that%20took%20place%20for%2014-15%20months%20disturbed%20the%20entire%20wrestling%20fraternity.%20Let%20alone%20one%20category%2C%20the%20wrestlers%20in%20other%20categories%20struggled%20as%20they%20could%20not%20practice%20without%20national%20and%20international%20tournaments.%20Hence%2C%20the%20wrestlers%20could%20not%20perform%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20Sanjay%20Singh%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Fsports%2Folympics%2Fstory%2Fparis-olympics-sanjay-singh-blames-wrestlers-protests-for-not-winning-enough-medals-2581956-2024-08-14%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndia%20Today%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20Vinesh%20and%20Aman%2C%20who%20both%20impressed%20in%20Paris%2C%20other%20wrestlers%20like%20Anshu%20Malik%20(57kg)%2C%20Reetika%20Hooda%20(76kg)%2C%20Nisha%20Dahiya%20(68kg)%20and%20Antim%20Panghal%20(53kg)%20failed%20to%20leave%20an%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20far%20as%20the%20verdict%20of%20Vinesh's%20silver%20medal%20plea%20at%20the%20Court%20of%20Arbitration%20for%20Sport%20(CAS)%20goes%2C%20a%20decision%20is%20expected%20by%20August%2016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECAS%20has%20established%20an%20ad%20hoc%20division%20in%20Paris%2C%20led%20by%20President%20Michael%20Lenard%20from%20the%20US%2C%20to%20handle%20Olympic%20cases.%20This%20division%20operates%20within%20the%20Paris%20judicial%20court%20in%20the%2017th%20arrondissement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVinesh%20Phogat%20was%20disqualified%20on%20the%20morning%20of%20the%20Paris%20Olympics%20final%20for%20exceeding%20the%2050kg%20weight%20limit.%20During%20the%20weigh-in%2C%20she%20was%20found%20to%20be%20100%20grams%20over%20the%20limit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20her%20disqualification%2C%20Phogat%20had%20on%20August%207%20requested%20CAS%20to%20award%20her%20the%20silver%20medal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECAS%20had%20previously%20extended%20the%20deadline%20to%20August%2013.%20Vinesh%20had%20reached%20the%20gold%20medal%20match%20by%20defeating%20Cuba's%20Yusneylis%20Guzman%20Lopez%205-0%20in%20the%20semi-finals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2029-year-old%20was%20set%20to%20face%20Sarah%20Ann%20Hildebrandt%20of%20the%20United%20States%20for%20the%20gold%20but%20was%20disqualified%20for%20the%20weight%20limit%20breach.%20A%20day%20after%20her%20disqualification%2C%20Vinesh%20also%20announced%20her%20decision%20to%20retire%20from%20wrestling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20ANI%20Inputs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723626840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fpv76mrno_vinesh-protest_625x300_14_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Folympics-2024%2Fwrestlers-protests-behind-ordinary-show-in-paris-olympics-federation-chief-sanjay-singh-6335266%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Wrestling%20Federation%20of%20India%20president%20Sanjay%20Singh%20has%20blamed%20wrestlers'%20protest%20behind%20their%20mediocre%20show%20at%20Paris%20Olympics.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I'm%2038%2C%20and%20one%20of%20my%20closest%20friends%20is%2072.%20We%20have%20more%20in%20common%20than%20you%20might%20think.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223517%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sarah%20Klein%20and%20her%20friend%20Carolyn%20smiling%20and%20looking%20at%20the%20camera.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66bb5b5d955b01c3294dfdfd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESarah%20Klein%20met%20her%20friend%20Carolyn%20while%20volunteering%20with%20FriendshipWorks.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Sarah%20Klein%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI%20moved%20from%20New%20York%20City%20to%20Boston%20and%20decided%20to%20volunteer%20to%20combat%20loneliness.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20was%20matched%20with%20Carolyn%2C%20who%20is%20more%20than%2030%20years%20older%20than%20I%20am.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOver%20time%2C%20we%20realized%20we%20cared%20about%20many%20of%20the%20same%20things%2C%20and%20we%20became%20friends.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20had%20planned%20to%20move%20back%20to%20my%20hometown%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcommuting-between-boston-and-new-york-via-seaplane-tailwind-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EBoston%20from%20New%20York%20City%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%202020%20with%20my%20now%20ex-husband%20to%20be%20closer%20to%20family%20long%20before%20we%20knew%20what%20was%20coming%20with%20the%20pandemic.%20Once%20I%20was%20finally%20there%2C%20I%20found%20myself%20working%20from%20home%2C%20taking%20walks%20through%20my%20eerily%20quiet%20neighborhood%2C%20ordering%20lots%20of%20takeout%2C%20and%20wondering%20how%20I%20would%20ever%20make%20new%20friends.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20so%20many%20social%20activities%20canceled%20and%20public%20spaces%20closed%2C%20I%20started%20volunteering%20with%20FriendshipWorks%2C%20a%20nonprofit%20that%20pairs%20volunteers%20with%20older%20adults%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmaking-friends-older-age-how-make-new-connections-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efight%20loneliness%20and%20isolation%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20I%20was%20trained%20to%20chat%20with%20an%20older%20adult%20over%20the%20phone%2C%20considering%20it%20wasn't%20currently%20safe%20to%20visit%20in%20person.%20I%20thought%20it%20sounded%20like%20a%20simple%20way%20to%20do%20some%20good%20in%20my%20new%20neighborhood.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20it%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20good%20for%20me%2C%20too.%20FriendshipWorks%20aims%20to%20address%20loneliness%20in%20older%20adults%2C%20but%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-culture-social-individualism-loneliness-epidemic-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eone-third%20of%20Americans%20are%20lonely%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20regardless%20of%20age.%20I%20know%20I%20was%2C%20with%20just%20a%20small%20social%20circle%20of%20family%20members%20and%20friends%20from%20growing%20up%20in%20the%20suburbs.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220f9023bf-d876-4839-b067-b0ddb620d3ab%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20match%20was%20almost%2030%20years%20older%20than%20I%20am%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20phone%20calls%20with%20my%20match%2C%20Carolyn%2C%20started%20in%20September%202020%20with%20small%20talk%20and%20getting-to-know-you%20questions.%20I%20learned%20she%20was%20approaching%20her%2070th%20birthday%20and%20had%20moved%20to%20Boston%20almost%2050%20years%20earlier%2C%20following%20some%20of%20her%20older%20siblings%20from%20their%20home%20in%20rural%20Georgia.%20Her%20local%20siblings%20had%20all%20since%20died.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDue%20to%20a%20number%20of%20health%20challenges%2C%20she%20had%20difficulty%20leaving%20her%20house%20and%20grew%20tired%20easily%20when%20she%20did.%20Carolyn's%20world%20was%20getting%20smaller%2C%20and%20one%20of%20her%20care%20providers%20suggested%20she%20contact%20FriendshipWorks%20to%20see%20if%20they%20could%20help.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20didn't%20meet%20in%20person%20until%20June%202021%2C%20after%20we'd%20been%20speaking%20over%20the%20phone%20weekly%20for%20nine%20months.%20Shortly%20thereafter%2C%20even%20though%20COVID%20restrictions%20were%20slowly%20lifting%20and%20I%20was%20exploring%20more%20of%20the%20city%2C%20my%20world%20started%20getting%20smaller%2C%20too%3A%20My%20brother%2C%20sister-in-law%2C%20and%20newborn%20nephew%20moved%20from%20Boston%20to%20Cleveland%20shortly%20after%20my%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frebuilding-my-life-after-painful-divorce-middle-age-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Emarriage%20unexpectedly%20ended%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20reality%20of%20my%20move%20to%20Boston%20no%20longer%20looked%20like%20I%20had%20imagined%20it%20would.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sarah%20Klein%20and%20her%20friend%20Carolyn%20sitting%20at%20a%20table%20and%20coloring%20in%20coloring%20books.%20They%20are%20smiling%20at%20each%20other.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66bb76935da406397bf563ad%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20and%20her%20friend%20Carolyn%20do%20things%20like%20color%20and%20walk%20together.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Sarah%20Klein%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229a39c224-90cb-41a5-9e1c-45c65cb048bd%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EOver%20time%2C%20we%20became%20genuine%20friends%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20was%20also%20when%20my%20relationship%20with%20Carolyn%20shifted%20from%20a%20volunteer%20opportunity%20to%20a%20genuine%20friendship.%20When%20I%20felt%20most%20adrift%2C%20it%20was%20grounding%20to%20know%20I%20had%20our%20weekly%20visit%20to%20look%20forward%20to.%20She%20has%20always%20been%20open%20about%20her%20own%20losses%2C%20sadness%2C%20and%20loneliness.%20It%20gave%20me%20permission%20to%20be%20open%20about%20mine.%20We%20could%20easily%20talk%20about%20family%2C%20relationships%2C%20or%20politics%20for%20nearly%20an%20hour%20straight%2C%20not%20knowing%20where%20the%20time%20went.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOur%20unconventional%20friendship%20wouldn't%20have%20happened%20if%20I%20hadn't