s%3Cp%3ESemiAnalysis%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ESemiAnalysis%20has%20grown%20from%20three%20analysts%20to%2012%20experts%20across%20five%20countries%20in%20two%20years.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20firm%20provides%20deep%20insight%20into%20GPUs%20and%20AI%20models%20and%20has%20become%20essential%20for%20major%20companies.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EChief%20analyst%20Dylan%20Patel%20said%20Nvidia's%20latest%20delay%20isn't%20shocking%2C%20but%20it%20will%20have%20a%20big%20impact.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%20CEO%20Jensen%20Huang%20isn't%20the%20only%20one%20who%20has%20gone%20from%20uber-nerd%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjensen-huang-signed-womans-chest-tech-conference-nvidia-rockstar-leather-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etech%20luminary%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20space%20of%20a%20few%20years.%20Dylan%20Patel%20may%20be%20less%20of%20a%20household%20name%2C%20but%20for%20those%20watching%20Huang's%20moves%20closely%2C%20Patel's%20firm%20SemiAnalysis%20has%20become%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-ai-chip-blackwell-delay-new-annual-product-launch-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecentral%20source%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20intel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20cofounder%20Sam%20Altman%20even%20called%20him%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-gemini-ai-model-smashes-gpt4-says-semianalysis-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethat%20semianalysis%20guy%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter%2C%20last%20year.%20Patel%20responded%20with%20an%20edited%20image%20of%20Google%20CEO%20Sundar%20Pichai%20pouring%20milk%20into%20Altman's%20mouth%20while%20holding%20him%20by%20the%20hair.%20Is%20there%20any%20greater%20sign%20of%20tech%20prowess%20than%20a%20high-profile%20online%20feud%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESemiAnalysis%20gets%20deep%20into%20the%20weeds%20on%20graphics%20processing%20units%2C%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-taiwan-china-chip-war-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebase%20of%20the%20supply%20chain%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20end-users%20building%20the%20AI%20models%20that%20require%20so%20many%20specialized%20chips.%20That%20exchange%20with%20Altman%20was%20just%20a%20year%20ago%2C%20but%20it%20might%20as%20well%20have%20been%20in%20a%20different%20lifetime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20two%20years%2C%20SemiAnalysis%20has%20grown%20from%20a%20team%20of%20three%20analysts%20in%20two%20countries%20to%20a%20team%20of%2012%20subject%20matter%20experts%20in%20the%20US%2C%20Japan%2C%20Singapore%2C%20Taiwan%2C%20and%20France.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20had%20some%20major%20companies%20that%20were%20customers%2C%20but%20now%20almost%20every%20major%20company%20in%20the%20AI%20infrastructure%2C%20server%2C%20model%2C%20space%20from%20sub-components%20all%20the%20way%20through%20to%20clouds%20and%20hyperscalers%20have%20become%20customers%2C%20which%20is%20a%20big%20shift%2C%26quot%3B%20Patel%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm's%20newsletter%2C%20launched%20in%202020%2C%20and%20its%20blog%20have%20become%20mandatory%20reading%20since%20they%20connect%20the%20semiconductor%20industry%20to%20the%20tech%20it%20enables%20in%20a%20way%20few%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENews%20that%20Nvidia's%20next%20chip%20launch%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-ai-chip-blackwell-delay-new-annual-product-launch-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBlackwell%2C%20would%20be%20delayed%3C%2Fa%3E%20stirred%20up%20many%20questions%20about%20how%20AI%20hardware%20from%20the%20largest%20player%20in%20the%20game%20is%20rolling%20out.%20Patel%20spoke%20to%20BI%20about%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20delay%2C%20and%20how%20to%20observe%20Nvidia%20like%20a%20pro.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20Q%26amp%3BA%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20clarity%20and%20length.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBI%3A%20Where%20do%20you%20get%20your%20information%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20consists%20of%20people%20across%20the%20entire%20supply%20chain%2C%20geographically%20and%20technically.%20We%20have%20someone%20who%20previously%20worked%20as%20low%20as%20ASML%20(Advanced%20Semiconductor%20Materials%20Lithography)%2C%20the%20largest%20equipment%20company%2C%20and%20then%20all%20the%20way%20through%20to%20companies%20upstream%2C%20such%20as%20former%20employees%20of%20Microsoft%2C%20Nvidia%2C%20etc.%20So%20we%20have%20the%20entire%20view%20of%20the%20supply%20chain%2C%20from%20manufacturing%2C%20up%20to%20models.%20Also%2C%20several%20people%20on%20the%20team%20are%20from%20hedge%20fund%20backgrounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20the%20team%20goes%20to%20more%20than%2050%20technical%20conferences%20across%20the%20entire%20stack%20%E2%80%94%20not%20just%20the%20trade%20shows%2C%20which%20are%20not%20really%20as%20valuable%2C%20but%20more%20the%20technical%20conferences%20where%20people%20are%20presenting%20papers%20and%20advancements%20in%20the%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20establish%20all%20these%20research%20and%20consulting%20relationships%2C%20you%20end%20up%20with%20a%20large%20well%20of%20information.%20That%20is%20how%20we're%20able%20to%20get%20disparate%20pieces%20of%20information%20that%20may%20be%20known%20and%20even%20common%20in%20one%20part%20of%20the%20supply%20chain%20but%20don't%20spread%20far%20outside%20it.%20Engineering%20especially%2C%20is%20very%20horizontal.%20Trying%20to%20draw%20the%20lines%20between%20all%20the%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20stack%20is%20very%20important.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBI%3A%20There%20was%20a%20recent%20report%20about%20Nvidia's%20next-generation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-ai-chip-blackwell-delay-new-annual-product-launch-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20Blackwell%20chip%20being%20delayed%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E.%20How%20common%20is%20a%20delay%20like%20this%20in%20the%20semi-world%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20semiconductor%20manufacturing%2C%20there's%20this%20loop%20of%20the%20design%20being%20sent%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchip-tsmc-taiwan-semiconductor-trillion-market-cap-nvidia-ai-asml-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETSMC%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20manufactures.%20Once%20you%20have%20the%20stencils%2C%20it's%20a%20multi-month%20process%20to%20produce%20chips.%20Then%20you%20send%20those%20wafers%20out%20to%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECustomers%20test%20them%20to%20make%20sure%20everything%20works.%20More%20often%20than%20not%2C%20it%20doesn't.%20Why%3F%20Take%2C%20for%20example%2C%20a%20modern%20iPhone%20chip.%20It%20has%2025%20billion%20transistors%20and%2015%20layers%20of%20metal.%20Twenty-five%20billion%20transistors%20are%2025%20billion%20on-off%20switches%2C%20and%20they're%20perfectly%20timed%20and%20organized%20so%20that%20everything%20you%20do%20on%20your%20iPhone%20happens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20chips%20are%20even%20more%20complicated%20than%20that.%20It's%20impossible%20to%20perfectly%20simulate%20everything%2C%20so%20you%20are%20always%20going%20to%20have%20issues.%20Then%20they'll%20need%20to%20make%20a%20few%20modifications%20to%20the%20design%20and%20send%20it%20back.%20That%20has%20always%20happened.%20And%20the%20range%20of%20modifications%20can%20be%20major%20to%20minor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%20has%20always%20had%20an%20incredibly%20aggressive%20timeline.%20They've%20always%20been%20really%20good%20about%20shipping%20either%20the%20first%20or%20second%20revision%20of%20the%20chip.%20Whereas%2C%20other%20companies%20can%20go%20through%2012%20revisions.%20Even%20big%20companies%20like%20AMD%20(Advanced%20Micro%20Devices)%20tend%20to%20go%20through%20two%2C%20or%20three%2C%20or%20four%20revisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fact%20that%20Nvidia%20wanted%20to%20ramp%20so%20fast%20%E2%80%94%20this%20Blackwell%20ramp%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20the%20first%20chip%20with%20%24100%20billion%20in%20sales%20%E2%80%94%20meant%20there%20were%20some%20minor%20delays.%20It's%20just%20a%20few%20months%20at%20most.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20because%20so%20many%20people%20are%20affected%20by%20that%20delay%2C%20it%20shakes%20the%20entire%20world.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20the%20customers%20affected%20by%20this%20would%20know%2C%20and%20it%20wouldn't%20shake%20up%20all%20the%20way%20to%20the%20top%20levels%20of%20every%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBI%3A%20What%20are%20your%20favorite%20non-revenue%20indicators%20to%20watch%20at%20Nvidia%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20is%20the%20size%20and%20use%20of%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20releases%20a%20new%20model%2C%20and%20it's%20now%20405%20billion%20parameters%2C%20right%3F%20These%20new%20models%20continue%20to%20increase%20the%20demand%20for%20compute%20voraciously.%20Now%20that%20Meta%20released%20this%20new%20model%2C%20and%20now%20that%20everyone%20uses%20these%20open-source%20models%20and%20doesn't%20develop%20their%20own%2C%20everyone%20switches%20to%20this%20bigger%2C%20newer%20model%2C%20and%20that%20creates%20a%20significant%20increase%20in%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20flip%20side%2C%20all%20the%20way%20downstream%2C%20companies%20in%20Taiwan%20have%20to%20report%20their%20revenue%20monthly.%20You%20can%20see%20the%20exact%20ramp%20of%20everything%20as%20soon%20as%20you%20want%20to%20see%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20there's%20a%20lot%20of%20information%20all%20the%20way%20upstream%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20models%20and%20deployments%2C%20and%20all%20the%20way%20downstream%20to%20the%20various%20sub-component%20suppliers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20place%20I%20like%20to%20look%20a%20lot%20is%20random%20suppliers%20that%20are%20very%20small%20in%20niche%20parts%20of%20the%20supply%20chain%2C%20or%20suppliers%20of%20suppliers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaybe%20Nvidia%20suppliers%20are%20very%20hush-hush%2C%20but%20maybe%20TSMC's%20suppliers%20are%20very%20open%20about%20what%20TSMC%20is%20ordering%20and%20you%20can%20estimate%20what's%20going%20to%20happen%20to%20Nvidia's%20production%20capacity%20or%20ability%20to%20sell%20servers%20from%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBI%3A%20Assuming%20the%20initial%20Blackwell%20rollout%20will%20indeed%20be%20smaller%20than%20promised%2C%20what%20do%20you%20know%20about%20who%20gets%20to%20be%20first%20in%20line%20for%20the%20new%20chips%3F%20And%20why%20do%20they%20get%20to%20be%20first%20in%20line%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHow%20Nvidia%20decides%20who%20gets%20to%20be%20first%20in%20line%20is%20a%20very%20complicated%20decision%20matrix%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20now%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-mergers-and-acquisition-startup-buying-spree-ftc-investigation-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einvestigation%20by%20the%20FTC%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20all%20sorts%20of%20reports%20that%20if%20you%20purchase%20their%20networking%20equipment%2C%20they%20will%20push%20you%20first%20in%20line%20or%20similar%20allegations%20like%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20the%20question%20is%20who%20are%20they%20going%20to%20prioritize%3F%20My%20sense%20is%20that%20customers%20who%20have%20no%20choice%20or%20are%20smaller%20and%2C%20therefore%20need%20more%20support%20from%20Nvidia%20would%20probably%20be%20de-prioritized%20relative%20to%20customers%20who%20are%20much%20larger%20and%20have%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20Microsoft%20and%20Meta%20are%20their%20two%20largest%20customers.%20They%20also%20have%20chip%20programs%20internally%2C%20but%20they're%20not%20as%20successful%20as%2C%20say%2C%20Amazon%20and%20especially%20Google.%20But%20they%20also%20went%20out%20and%20bought%20AMD%20GPUs.%20If%20you're%20Nvidia%2C%20it%20makes%20sense%20to%20prioritize%20your%20biggest%20customers%20because%20th