3Cp%3EIn%20a%20bizarre%20incident%20that%20has%20left%20the%20aviation%20community%20stunned%2C%20pilots%20on%20a%20Boeing%20747%20flight%20from%20Jeddah%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia%20to%20Abuja%2C%20Nigeria%20witnessed%20and%20filmed%20multiple%20unidentified%20flying%20objects%20(UFOs)%20performing%20impossible%20maneuvers%20in%20the%20night%20sky.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2024%2F08%2F13%2Flifestyle%2Fboeing-747-pilots-record-multiple-ufos-dancing-in-ways-planes-cant%2F%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%C2%A0Captain%20Ruud%20Van%20Pangemanan%2C%20a%20seasoned%20pilot%20and%20vlogger%2C%20was%20operating%20the%20flight%20when%20the%20extraordinary%20phenomenon%20occurred%20at%205%20a.m.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Captain%20said%20that%20he%20witnessed%20an%20extremely%20vivid%2C%20star-like%20object%20that%20appeared%20to%20be%20''dancing''%20in%20the%20sky.%20The%20'UFO'%20exhibited%20rapid%20and%20unpredictable%20altitude%20changes%2C%20plunging%20quickly%20before%20abruptly%20returning%20to%20its%20original%20height%2C%20leaving%20him%20stunned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UFO's%20erratic%20movements%20become%20even%20more%20bizarre%2C%20breaking%20off%20in%20random%20directions.%20''The%20light%20of%20the%20UFO%20in%20front%20of%20us%20moves%20freely.%20Sometimes%20forward%2C%20sometimes%20backwards%2C%20sometimes%20left%2C%20right%2C%20or%20vice%20versa%2C''%20the%20pilot%20said.%20The%20object's%20bright%20light%20was%20also%20seen%20flickering%20at%20times%20and%20fully%20disappeared%20during%20moments%20as%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWatch%20the%20video%20here%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F86L3UYZAeys%3Fsi%3DSI0ADGEiP99oezym%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20footage%20shared%20by%20the%20Captain%C2%A0recorded%20at%20least%20three%20bright%20objects%2C%C2%A0eerily%20reminiscent%20of%20the%20infamous%20Phoenix%20Lights%20incident%20in%201997.%20However%2C%20the%20pilot%2C%20claimed%20that%20he%20saw%20up%20to%20four%20objects%2C%20and%20also%C2%A0ruled%20out%20any%20Earthly%20possibilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''We%20thought%20the%20light%20was%20a%20plane%20but%20it%20wasn't%20on%20our%20radar.%20Then%20we%20thought%20maybe%20it%20was%20a%20star%20but%20the%20stars%20twinkled%20quickly%20and%20the%20stars%20didn't%20move%2C''%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECaptain%20Van%20Pangemanan%20further%20ruled%20out%20the%20possibility%20of%20the%20object%20being%20a%20satellite.%20''It%20is%20impossible%20for%20a%20satellite%20to%20move%20like%20that%2C''%20he%20stated%2C%20citing%20the%20object's%20erratic%20movements.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20the%20video%2C%20one%20user%20wrote%2C%20''Dear%20Captain%20Ruud%2C%20Thank%20you%20for%20sharing%20this%20video.%20The%20flight%20was%20spectacular.%20The%20sighting%20of%20the%20UAP%20Craft%20is%20more%20reason%20to%20believe%20we%20are%20not%20alone.%20May%20you%2C%20your%20copilot%2C%20and%20aircrew%20always%20have%20safe%20flights%20around%20the%20world.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20commented%2C%20''Thanks%20for%20this%20Captain%20Rudd%20and%20crew.%20Gone%20are%20the%20days%20when%20Airline%20pilots%20and%20crews%20had%20to%20shut%20up%20about%20reporting%20unusual%20objects%20in%20the%20sky.%20These%20things%20are%20real%2C%20and%20reporting%20them%20may%20help%20to%20at%20least%20plot%20where%20they%20are%20most%20prevalent.%20This%20in%20turn%20alerts%20others%20to%20be%20cautious.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723622160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fk4kf7748_ufo-sighting_625