2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Fsc-stays-nclat-order-that-allowed-bcci-to-settle-its-dues-with-byjus%2Farticleshow%2F112517292.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Karnataka%20School%20Teacher%20Tries%20To%20Rape%20Student%20In%20Class%2C%20Arrested%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20have%20arrested%20a%20teacher%20for%20attempting%20to%20rape%20an%2011-year-old%20schoolgirl%20in%20the%20classroom%20in%20Karnataka's%20Kalaburagi%20district%2C%20said%20officials%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20was%20reported%20from%20a%20government%20school%20located%20in%20the%20limits%20of%20Nimbarga%20police%20station%20in%20Aland%20taluk%20of%20the%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20police%2C%20the%20victim%20was%20studying%20in%20Class%205%20in%20the%20school.%20The%20accused%20attacked%20her%20when%20the%20girl%20had%20gone%20to%20the%20classroom%20after%20having%20a%20midday%20meal%20on%20Tuesday.%20The%20girl%20was%20alone%20in%20the%20classroom%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20assault.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accused%20threatened%20her%20not%20to%20make%20noise%20and%20attempted%20to%20rape%20her.%20However%2C%20when%20the%20girl%20resisted%20and%20started%20screaming%20for%20help%2C%20the%20accused%20teacher%20fled%20from%20the%20school%20premises.%20The%20victim%20went%20to%20her%20home%20and%20informed%20her%20parents%20about%20the%20incident%2C%20the%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20parents%20first%20questioned%20the%20headmaster%20about%20the%20incident%20and%20then%20filed%20a%20complaint%20with%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Nimbarga%20police%20launched%20a%20hunt%20for%20the%20accused%20teacher%20and%20later%20arrested%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20have%20registered%20the%20case%20under%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Children%20from%20Sexual%20Offences%20Act%20(POCSO)%20and%20other%20sections%20under%20the%20Bhartiya%20Nyay%20Sanhita%20(BNS).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20case%20has%20increased%20the%20concerns%20of%20the%20people%20in%20the%20district%20which%20has%20seen%20a%20rise%20in%20the%20POCSO%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20data%20showed%20that%20the%20cases%20of%20rape%20against%20minors%20have%20increased%20by%20three%20times%20those%20of%20cases%20reported%20on%20women%20in%20the%20district%20in%20the%20past%20three%20years%2C%20according%20to%20police%20sources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20of%20gang%20rape%20of%20a%2013-year-old%20girl%20reported%20in%20June%20had%20triggered%20protests%20and%20roadblocks%20in%20the%20region.%20The%20victim%20was%20found%20to%20be%20eight%20months%20pregnant%20during%20the%20treatment.%20Later%2C%20she%20died%20in%20the%20hospital%20of%20multi-organ%20failure.%20The%20girl%20was%20allegedly%20raped%20by%20the%20accused%20for%20several%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kalaburgi%20district%20is%20the%20native%20of%20Congress%20national%20President%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20and%20his%20son%2C%20Minister%20for%20RDPR%2C%20IT%20and%20BT%20Priyank%20Kharge%20is%20also%20the%20in-charge%20district%20minister.%20Medical%20Education%20Minister%20Sharan%20Prakash%20Patil%20also%20hails%20from%20Kalaburagi%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20also%20comes%20days%20after%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkolkata-doctor-rape-murder-rg-kar-medical-college-why-kolkata-doctors-rape-murder-case-went-to-cbi-courts-tough-remarks-6333533%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topscroll%5C%22%3Erape%20and%20murder%20of%20a%20doctor%20at%20Kolkata's%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%3C%2Fa%3E%20shook%20the%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723621200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fvu42decg_karnataka-police-generic_625x300_14_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkarnataka-school-teacher-tries-to-rape-11-year-old-student-in-class-arrested-6334499%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20police%20have%20arrested%20a%20teacher%20for%20attempting%20to%20rape%20an%2011-year-old%20schoolgirl%20in%20the%20classroom%20in%20Karnataka's%20Kalaburagi%20district%2C%20said%20officials%20on%20Wednesday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkarnataka-school-teacher-tries-to-rape-11-year-old-student-in-class-arrested-6334499%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Was%20Vinesh%20Phogat%20Case%20Verdict%20Delayed%3F%20Here's%20What%20Lawyer%20Told%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Court%20of%20Arbitration%20for%20Sport%20(CAS)%20announced%20a%20fresh%20deadline%20to%20deliver%20the%20verdict%20on%20Indian%20wrestler%20Vinesh%20Phogat's%20appeal%20on%20Tuesday.%20Vinesh%20and%20her%20fans%20all%20across%20India%20might%20have%20to%20wait%20till%20August%2016%20to%20hear%20from%20the%20court%20after%20the%20wrestler%20appealed%20for%20a%20silver%20medal%20to%20be%20granted%20to%20her%20following%20her%20disqualification%20from%20the%20Women's%2050kg%20freestyle%20final%20over%20failed%20weigh-in.%20While%20a%20delay%20in%20the%20verdict%20signals%20Vinesh's%20strengthening%20grip%20on%20the%20case%2C%20the%20court%20also%20has%20to%20consider%20the%20ramifications%20of%20the%20verdict%2C%20if%20given%20in%20the%20wrestler's%20favour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Vinesh%20does%20get%20a%20joint-silver%20medal%20despite%20weighing%20100%20grams%20more%20on%20the%20morning%20of%20her%20final%2C%20the%20verdict%20is%20likely%20to%20change%20the%20way%20wrestling%20as%20a%20sport%20will%20be%20played%20in%20future%20editions%20of%20the%20Olympic%20Games.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20been%20learned%20that%20the%20court%20doesn't%20want%20to%20rush%20into%20a%20decision%20and%20want%20to%20analyse%20every%20single%20detail%2C%20hence%20the%20delay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EArguments%20Made%20By%20Vinesh%20Phogat's%20Counsel%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVinesh's%20counsel%2C%20in%20front%20of%20the%20sole%20arbitrar%20Dr.%20Annabelle%20Bennett%2C%20highlighted%20the%20negligible%20advantage%20over%20100%20gram%20weight%20gain%20among%20multiple%20arguments.%20As%20the%20wait%20continues%2C%20here%20are%20the%20arguments%20made%20by%20Vinesh's%20counsel%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20excess%20of%20100g%20is%20extremely%20negligible%20(representing%20around%200.1%20to%200.2%20percent%20of%20the%20athlete's%20weight)%20and%20can%20easily%20be%20caused%20by%20the%20bloating%20of%20a%20human%20body%20during%20summer%20weather%2C%20as%20the%20heat%20makes%20the%20human%20body%20retain%20more%20water%2C%20scientifically%20for%20survival%20purposes.%20It%20can%20also%20be%20due%20to%20muscle%20mass%20increase%20as%20the%20athlete%20competed%20three%20times%20on%20the%20same%20day.%20It%20can%20also%20be%20caused%20by%20the%20food%20consumption%20of%20the%20athlete%20after%20the%20competitions%20to%20sustain%20her%20health%20and%20integrity%20for%20the%20demanding%20competitions%2C%26quot%3B%20Vinesh's%20counsel%20had%20submitted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20would%20be%20a%20manifest%20disproportion%20between%20the%20level%20of%20excess%20(which%20excludes%20any%20attempt%20at%20fraud%20or%20manipulation%20of%20the%20athlete)%20and%20the%20irreversible%20consequences%20that%20would%20result%20from%20her%20non-participation%20in%20the%20finals%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20deprivation%20of%20her%20silver%20medal%20that%20was%20acquired%20by%20hard%20work.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVinesh%20had%20reached%20the%20gold%20medal%20match%20in%20Paris%20Olympics%20by%20defeating%20Cuba's%20Yusneylis%20Guzman%20Lopez%205-0%20in%20the%20semi-finals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20wrestler%20was%20set%20to%20face%20Sarah%20Ann%20Hildebrandt%20of%20the%20United%20States%20in%20th