rged%20people%20who%20had%20received%20confectionaries%20from%20the%20Auckland%20charity%20not%20to%20consume%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20know%20how%20widespread%20it%20is.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20candy%20was%20donated%20anonymously%20by%20a%20member%20of%20the%20public%2C%20the%20charity%20said%2C%20in%20a%20sealed%20branded%20package.%20The%20sweets%20were%20then%20distributed%20into%20food%20parcels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20potential%20for%20New%20Zealand%20that%20there%20is%20a%20lethal%20substance%20dressed%20up%20as%20a%20lolly%20(sweet)%2C%26quot%3B%20Helen%20Robinson%20from%20Auckland%20City%20Mission%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20to%20work%20on%20the%20assumption%20that%20this%20was%20a%20kind%20of%20batch.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20charity%20believes%20up%20to%20400%20people%20could%20have%20received%20the%20affected%20sweets%20in%20a%20food%20package.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERobinson%20said%20so%20far%20eight%20separate%20families%20had%20been%20affected%2C%20but%20no%20one%20had%20yet%20been%20hospitalised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20knew%20of%20an%20instance%20where%20a%20parent%20gave%20one%20of%20the%20candies%20to%20her%20child%2C%20who%20immediately%20spat%20it%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERobinson%20said%20she%20had%20been%20told%20the%20potent%20contaminated%20sweets%20tasted%20%26quot%3Bacrid%20and%20revolting%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20could%20have%20only%20a%20very%20small%20touch%20or%20lick%20of%20the%20substance%20and%20still%20be%20deeply%20affected%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20warned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20contaminated%20sweet%20was%20taken%20for%20testing%20when%20a%20person%20felt%20strange%20after%20starting%20to%20eat%20it%20and%20noticed%20a%20bitter%20taste.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMethamphetamine%20can%20cause%20chest%20pain%2C%20racing%20heart%2C%20seizures%2C%20delirium%20and%20loss%20of%20consciousness%2C%20the%20drug%20foundation%20warned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHelm%20told%20Radio%20New%20Zealand%20it%20is%20common%20for%20drug%20smugglers%20to%20hide%20illegal%20narcotics%20in%20food%20form.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20suspect%20somebody%20hasn't%20intentionally%20sought%20to%20poison%20children.%20It%20will%20be%20up%20to%20police%20to%20determine%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added%20in%20the%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723615260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2016-07%2Fdrug-abuse-istock-650_650x400_41469624488.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Flethal-amount-of-meth-found-hidden-in-sweets-in-new-zealand-probe-underway-6332877%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pineapple%20sweets%20dished%20out%20by%20a%20New%20Zealand%20charity%20have%20tested%20positive%20for%20potentially%20lethal%20amounts%20of%20methamphetamine%2C%20police%20said%20Wednesday%2C%20sparking%20an%20urgent%20race%20to%20remove%20them%20from%20the%20streets.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Flethal-amount-of-meth-found-hidden-in-sweets-in-new-zealand-probe-underway-6332877%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Weather%20presenter%20speaks%20out%20about%20on-air%20panic%20attack%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723615183000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F3611%2Flive%2F64e9b640-5a01-11ef-8f0f-0577398c3339.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fvideos%2Fckgwddzeyero%232%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22ABC%20News%20Breakfast's%20Nate%20Byrne%20speaks%20with%20the%20BBC%20about%20how%20he%20handled%20the%20on-air%20moment.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3