aughter%20and%20little%20granddaughter%20like%20millions%20of%20Bengali%20families.%20We%20must%20rise%20to%20the%20occasion.%20Enough%20of%20cruelty%20against%20women.%20Let's%20resist%20together.%20Come%20what%20may%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20post%20late%20last%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20a%20'X'%20user%20said%20the%20senior%20leader%20may%20be%20thrown%20out%20of%20Trinamool%20Congress%20for%20joining%20a%20protest%20against%20his%20own%20government%2C%20he%20responded%2C%20%26quot%3BPlease%20need%20not%20worry%20for%20my%20fate.%20Blood%20of%20a%20freedom%20fighter%20flows%20in%20my%20veins.%20I'm%20least%20bothered.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ETomorrow%20I%20am%20going%20to%20join%20the%20protesters%20particularly%20because%20I've%20a%20daughter%20and%20little%20granddaughter%20like%20millions%20of%20Bengali%20families.%20We%20must%20rise%20to%20the%20occasion.%20Enough%20of%20cruelty%20against%20women.%20Let's%20resist%20together.%20Come%20what%20may.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Sukhendu%20Sekhar%20Ray%20(%40Sukhendusekhar)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSukhendusekhar%2Fstatus%2F1823414326042235051%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2013%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2075-year-old%20has%20been%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Upper%20House%20of%20Parliament%20since%202011%20and%20has%20also%20served%20as%20Deputy%20Leader%20of%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20in%20the%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWomen%20in%20Kolkata%20and%20other%20parts%20of%20Bengal%20will%20take%20to%20the%20streets%20late%20tonight%20as%20part%20of%20a%20massive%20protest%20against%20the%20doctor's%20rape%20and%20murder%20at%20the%20state-run%20hospital.%20The%20protest%2C%20which%20will%20begin%20at%2011.55%20pm%2C%20has%20been%20described%20as%2C%20%26quot%3BFor%20women's%20independence%20on%20the%20midnight%20of%20independence%2