dy%3B%20it%20was%20a%20real%20downer%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20she%20has%20performed%20at%20over%20300%20open%20mics%20at%20different%20venues%2C%20including%20Boka%20Book%20Cafe%2C%20Vintage%20Comedy%20Club%2C%20Classic%20Rock%20Cafe%2C%20Space%20Comedy%20Club%2C%20Hippie%20at%20Heart%20and%20The%20Comedy%20Clubhouse%20in%20Pune%20and%20has%20been%20an%20advocate%20for%20disability%20inclusion%20for%20over%20a%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-21_11zon-1723470978.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sweta%20wanted%20to%20prove%20that%20people%20with%20disabilities%20can%20not%20only%20make%20jokes%20but%20also%20laugh%20at%20themselves.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-21_11zon-1723470978.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-21_11zon-1723470978-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-21_11zon-1723470978-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-21_11zon-1723470978-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-21_11zon-1723470978-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-360955%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESweta%20wanted%20to%20prove%20that%20people%20with%20disabilities%20can%20not%20only%20make%20jokes%20but%20also%20laugh%20at%20themselves.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%E2%80%99s%20a%20running%20joke%20in%20my%20family%2C%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20