more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20has%20reinforced%20my%20passion%20for%20space%20exploration.%20I%20have%20a%20clear%20vision%20of%20my%20academic%20and%20career%20goals%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20Class%2011%20student%20at%2021K%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20won%20the%20Right%20Stuff%20award%2C%20given%20to%20an%20outstanding%20camper%20who%20excels%20not%20only%20in%20skills%20and%20tasks%20but%20also%20embodies%20an%20exceptional%20attitude%2C%20team%20spirit%2C%20and%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20aims%20to%20pursue%20a%20Bachelors%20degree%20in%20astrophysics%20at%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Science%20(IISc)%20or%C2%A0Indian%20Institute%20of%20Science%20Education%20and%20Research%20(IISER)%20or%20at%20the%20Massachusetts%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20(MIT).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20how%20you%20could%20also%20enrol%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rocketcenter.com%2FSpaceCamp%2FAdvancedAcademy%23block-usrcapiblock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espace%20camp%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%2C%20Images%20Courtesy%3A%20Geet%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723210097000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fgeett-1723203096.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D360476%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Geet%2C%20a%20student%20of%20Class%2011%20from%20Delhi%20participated%20in%20the%20NASA%20Space%20Camp%20at%20the%20US%20Space%20and%20Rocket%20Center%20in%20June%202024.%20Geet%20was%20just%20five%20when%20she%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20space.%20What%20followed%20soon%20was%20her%20ambition%20to%20become%20an%20astrophysicist.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F360476%2Fnasa-space-camp-for-students-astronauts-geet-alabama-us-space-rocket-centre-how-to-get-apply%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Startup%20Uses%20Corn%20Waste%20to%20Make%20Bags%20That%20Decompose%20in%20180%20Days%3B%20Replaced%206%20Million%20Plastic%20Bags%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20midst%20of%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20when%20his%20peers%20engaged%20themselves%20in%20making%20social%20media%20content%2C%20Mohammed%20Azhar%20Mohiuddin%20saw%20this%20as%20an%20opportunity%20to%20delve%20into%20entrepreneurship%20and%20tackle%20pressing%20issues%20such%20as%20plastic%20pollution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20a%20young%20age%2C%20he%20dabbled%20in%20various%20ventures%20from%20website%20development%2C%20logo%20designing%2C%20to%20running%20a%20cloud%20kitchen%20to%20selling%20burgers%20from%20home.%20His%20entrepreneurial%20spirit%20was%20fueled%20by%20a%20desire%20to%20solve%20problems%20rather%20than%20solely%20chasing%20financial%20gains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%202019%2C%20I%20wondered%20what%20I%20was%20really%20even%20chasing.%20Money%3F%20That%20would%20come%20even%20after%20I%20started%20focusing%20on%20solving%20real%20life%20problems%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20researching%20on%20top%20global%20environmental%20issues%2C%20Azhar%20found%20that%20there%20have%20been%20several%20awareness%20campaigns%20and%20protests%20worldwide%20on%20plastic%20pollution.%20%E2%80%9CUnless%20we%20have%20an%20alternative%2C%20there%20is%20no%20way%20to%20curb%20plastic%20usage.%20While%20big%20brands%20can%20afford%20jute%20and%20cloth%20bags%20but%20medium%20and%20small%20businesses%20which%20comprise%20a%20bulk%20of%20the%20Indian%20market%20continue%20to%20use%20plastic%20bags%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20major%20reasons%20behind%20the%20extensive%20use%20of%20plastic%20bags%20are%20its%20properties.%20It%20is%20water%20resistant%2C%20thermal%2C%20durable%2C%20light-weight%2C%20and%20has%20good%20tensile%20strength.%20I%20wanted%20to%20find%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F352330%2Fbubble-wrap-replacement-in-india-coconut-coir-sustainable-packaging-startup-seaweed-innovation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20solution%20that%20could%20mirror%20the%20properties%20of%20plastic%20while%20being%20eco-friendly%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20cheaper%20than%20paper%2C%20cloth%2C%20and%20jute%20alternatives%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20quest%20led%20him%20to%20launch%20%E2%80%98Bio%20Reform%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20Hyderabad-based%20startup%20that%20manufactures%20compostable%20bags%20using%20corn%20waste%2C%20sugars%2C%20cellulose%2C%20and%20other%20natural%20components%20into%20sustainable%20biopolymers.%20In%20the%20past%20two%20years%2C%20it%20has%20replaced%20over%20six%20million%20plastic%20bags.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FBioreform-1-1723181120.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Azhar%20is%20manufacturing%20eco-friendly%20carry%20bags%2C%20biomedical%20waste%20bags%2C%20garbage%20bags%2C%20food%20pouches%2C%20and%20book%20wraps.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FBioreform-1-1723181120.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FBioreform-1-1723181120-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FBioreform-1-1723181120-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FBioreform-1-1723181120-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FBioreform-1-1723181120-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-360465%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAzhar%20manufactures%20eco-friendly%20carry%20bags%2C%20biomedical%20waste%20bags%2C%20garbage%20bags%2C%20food%20pouches%2C%20and%20book%20wraps.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EChallenges%20on%20the%20way%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAzhar%20drew%20his%20inspiration%20from%20a%20biopolymer%20research%20paper%20dating%20back%20to%20the%201800s.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20started%20studying%20about%20a%20biodegradable%20polymer%2C%20PBAT%20(Polybutylene%20adipate-co-terephthalate)%2C%20that%20is%20derived%20from%20plant-based%20sources%20such%20as%20corn%20and%20potatoes.%20This%20formed%20the%20basis%20of%20a%20new%20business%20endeavour%20for%20Azhar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20step%20was%20to%20find%20the%20right%20machinery%20to%20process%20the%20raw%20materials%20into%20end%20products.%20His%20determination%20was%20tested%20when%20he%20faced%20several%20setbacks%20such%20as%20encountering%20fraudulent%20schemes%20and%20operational%20difficulties%20in%20the%20early%20stages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20uncle%20and%20I%20went%20to%20Delhi%20to%20check%20the%20machinery%20after%20we%20came%20to%20know%20a%20seemingly%20promising%20opportunity%20but%20it%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20scam.%20The%20contact%20person%20was%20not%20answering%20our%20calls%20and%20his%20promised%20location%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20barren%20land.%20It%20was%20very%20traumatising%20for%20us.%20I%20had%20somehow%20convinced%20my%20parents%20and%20now%20I%20did%20not%20want%20to%20go%20back%20home%20empty-handed%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDetermined%20not%20to%20let%20this%20setback%20deter%20them%2C%20Azhar%20and%20his%20uncle%20took%20a%20leap%20of%20faith%20and%20reached%20out%20to%20another%20contact%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20which%20came%20with%20its%20own%20series%20of%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELanding%20during%20a%20curfew%20amidst%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20Azhar%20had%20to%20spend%20most%20of%20the%20night%20stranded%20on%20the%20road%20as%20the%20hotel%20denied%20check-in%20due%20to%20a%20sudden%20RT-PCR%20report%20requirement.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20the%20perseverance%20paid%20off%20when%20we%20witnessed%20the%20machinery%20and%20its%20live%20demonstration%20the%20next%20morning%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%20the%20same%20time%2C%20he%20received%20Rs%201%20crore%20funding%20from%20the%20Adventure%20Park%20incubator%20programme.%20In%20early%202022%2C%20he%20inaugurated%20his%20factory%20in%20Hyderabad%20at%20the%20age%20of%2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FBioreform-3-1723181261.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%202022%2C%20Azhar%20inaugurated%20his%20factory%20in%20Hyderabad.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FBioreform-3-1723181261.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FBioreform-3-1723181261-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FBioreform-3-1723181261-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FBioreform-3-1723181261-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FBioreform-3-1723181261-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-360466%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIn%202022%2C%20Azhar%20inaugurated%20his%20factory%20in%20Hyderabad.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EReplaced%206%20million%20plastic%20bags%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESetting%20up%20a%20manufacturing%20unit%20from%20scratch%20was%20itself%20challenging%20for%20Azhar.%20He%20had%20to%20manage%20the%20intricacies%20of%20a%20manufacturing%20business%20and%20the%20pressures%20of%20balancing%20academic%20commitments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20the%20inauguration%20day%2C%20my%20uncle%2C%20who%20was%20also%20the%20co-founder%2C%20quit%20the%20company%20citing%20some%20personal%20reasons.%20I%20tried%20to%20balance%20both%20my%20studies%20and%20the%20operations%20of%20the%20company%20%E2%80%93%20from%20collecting%20raw%20material%2C%20assisting%20workers%20to%20manufacture%20bags%2C%20delivering%20the%20products%20in%20the%20market.%20I%20used%20to%20sleep%20in%20a%20corner%20in%20the%20factory%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Azhar%2C%20who%20was%20then%20in%20the%20third%20year%20of%20his%20college.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20continued%20for%20a%20year%20but%20Azhar%20had%20to%20shut%20the%20factory%20down%20after%20he%20was%20unable%20to%20make%20profits%20to%20sustain%20the%20company.%20%E2%80%9CI%20came%20back%20to%20zero.%20Meanwhile%2C%20I%20had%2014-15%20backlogs%20in%20my%20engineering.%20In%20a%20bid%20to%20balance%20both%20jobs%2C%20I%20failed%20at%20both.%20It%20was%20a%20stressful%20situation%20for%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20through%20sheer%20grit%20and%20relentless%20effort%2C%20the%20civil%20engineer%20not%20only%20cleared%20all%20exams%20but%20also%20secured%20a%20funding%20from%20an%20investor%2C%20and%20eventually%20revived%20his%20enterprise%20in%20a%20couple%20of%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20his%20company%20is%20manufacturing%204-5%20lakh%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F345783%2Fyellowbag-in-madurai-traditional-tamil-cloth-bags-plastic-waste-krishnan-subramanian-gowri-gopinath-earn-crores%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecarry%20bags%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20biomedical%20waste%20bags%2C%20garbage%20bags%2C%20food%20pouches%2C%20and%20book%20wraps.%20Interestingly%2C%20Azhar%20says%2C%20these%20bags%20are%20compostable%20and%20can%20be%20decomposed%20within%20180%20days.%20In%20the%20last%20two%20years%2C%20his%20startup%20has%20replaced%20more%20than%20six%20million%20plastic%20bags%20by%20commercialising%20in%20the%20B2B%20chain.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20he%20clocked%20an%20annual%20revenue%20of%20Rs%201.8%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMohd%20Sami%20Uddin%2C%20co-founder%20of%20Country%20Chicken%20Co%2C%20has%20been%20using%20Bio%20Reform%20bags%20for%20more%20than%20a%20year.%20Sharing%20his%20feedback%2C%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20wanted%20to%20focus%20on%20sustainable%20packaging%20as%20much%20as%20possible.%20Prior%20to%20Bio%20Reform%20bags%2C%20we%20were%20using%20plastic%20bags.%20Later%20on%2C%20we%20also%20tried%20other%20sustainable%20bags%20but%20unfortunately%2C%20they%20were%20neither%20food%20grade%20quality%20nor%20superior.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20times%2C%20the%20customers%20would%20complain%20to%20us%20if%20some%20sharp%20bones%20would%20pop%20out%20from%20low-grade%20bags.%20However%2C%20Bio%20Reform%20bags%20meet%20all%20our%20requirements%20and%20can%20be%20easily%20sealed%20as%20well%2C%20similar%20to%20plastic.%20Besides%2C%20there%20was%20not%20much%20difference%20from%20the%20price%C2%A0%20point%20also.%20The%20plastic%20bags%20would%20cost%20us%20Rs%20160%20per%20kg%20whereas%20Bio%20Reform%20bags%20cost%20Rs%20180%20per%20kg%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20individual%20level%2C%20Azhar%20says%20that%20he%20has%20spearheaded%20a%20movement%20towards%20India%E2%80%99s%20vision%20to%20become%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F289750%2Findia-bans-single-use-plastics-eco-friendly-alternatives-cups-cutlery%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esingle-use%20plastic%3C%2Fa%3E-free.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIssues%20related%20to%20plastic%20pollution%20are%20not%20limited%20to%20affecting%20aquatic%20life%20and%20animals%20anymore.%20Today%2C%20microplastic%20has%20reached%20our%20bloodstream.%20Bottled%20water%20contains%20microplastics.%20Addressing%20this%20is%20an%20important%20and%20urgent%20problem%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20glad%20I%20am%20able%20to%20contribute%20my%20part.%20It%20is%20sometimes%20taxing%20to%20not%20lead%20a%20regular%20college%20life%20but%20in%20the%20end%2C%20it%20is%20all%20worth%20it.%20I%20feel%20content%20when%20I%20go%20back%20to%20sleep.%20But%20much%20more%20needs%20to%20be%20done%20to%20make%20India%20plastic-free%2C%20and%20I%20will%20continue%20to%20strive%20for%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Mohammed%20Azhar.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723208510000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FBioreform-1-1723181120.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D360462%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mohammed%20Azhar%20Mohiuddin's%20company%20'Bio%20Reform'%20uses%20innovative%20biotechnology%20processes%20to%20manufacture%20eco-friendly%2C%20biodegradable%2C%20and%20compostable%20bags%20that%20decompose%20within%20180%20days.%20Here's%20how%20they%20are%20replacing%20plastic%20bags.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A62%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F360462%2Feco-friendly-biodegradable-bags-plastic-bag-replacement-bioreform-startup-hyderabad%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20an%20Indian%20Manufacturing%20Company%20Meets%2075%25%20of%20Its%20Energy%20Requirements%20Using%20Renewable%20Sources%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20has%20been%20published%20in%20partnership%20with%20Merino%20Industries.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESustainability%20isn%E2%80%99t%20an%20end%20goal%2C%20it%20is%20a%20mindset.%20This%20philosophy%20is%20championed%20by%20Merino%20Industries%20Limited%20(MIL)%2C%20one%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20manufacturers%20of%20decorative%20laminates%2C%20restroom%20cubicles%2C%20modular%20furniture%20and%20surfacing%20solutions.%20Their%20commitment%20to%20eco-friendly%20energy%20alternatives%20sets%20a%20precedent%20for%20other%20industries%20on%20how%20operations%20can%20be%20conducted%20without%20harming%20the%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Mr%20Prakash%20Lohia%2C%20CMD%2C%20Merino%20Industries%2C%20the%20transition%20from%20conventional%20energy%20sources%20like%20fossil%20fuels%20to%20green%20alternatives%20has%20not%20been%20without%20challenges.%20However%2C%20the%20key%20lies%20in%20implementing%20measurable%20changes%20at%20every%20stage%20of%20operation%2C%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20where%20the%20%E2%80%98Nirmal%20Sustainability%20Program%E2%80%99%20steps%20in.%20The%20initiative%20is%20thoughtfully%20designed%20and%20catalyses%20Merino%E2%80%99s%20commitment%20to%20becoming%20a%20sustainable%20and%20responsible%20industry.%20The%20programme%20hinges%20on%20scaling%20business%20growth%20alongside%20societal%20prosperity%20and%20pro-environmental%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20laser%20focus%20on%20increased%20utilisation%20of%20green%20energy%2C%20water%20conservation%2C%20air%20pollution%20reduction%2C%20circular%20economy%2C%20waste%20recycling%2C%20large-scale%20plantation%2C%20and%20the%20implementation%20of%20organic%20manure%20in%20agro-farming%2C%20the%20company%20is%20attempting%20to%20achieve%20the%20overarching%20goal%20of%20continuously%20reducing%20its%20carbon%20footprint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20commitment%20to%20eco-consciousness%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMerino%20strives%20that%20wealth%20is%20generated%20with%20minimalistic%20harm%20to%20the%20environment.%20To%20understand%20how%20it%20is%20achieving%20this%2C%20it%20is%20crucial%20to%20take%20a%20look%20at%20its%20%E2%80%98Triple%20Bottom%20Line%20Framework%E2%80%99%20that%20encompasses%20three%20key%20dimensions%20%E2%80%94%20Environmental%2C%20Social%2C%20and%20Financial%20impacts.%20Success%20follows%20when%20each%20parameter%20is%20scaled%20in%20parallel%20to%20the%20other.%20Excellence%20lies%20at%20the%20convergence%20of%20economy%20and%20sustainability%2C%20they%20believe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-1723194040.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20integrated%20factory%20and%20farm%20at%20Hapur%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-1723194040.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-1723194040-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-1723194040-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-1723194040-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-1723194040-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-360477%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20integrated%20factory%20and%20farm%20at%20Hapur.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-1-1723194179.jpg%5C%22%20width