0https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-8_11zon-1723195056-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-8_11zon-1723195056-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-360492%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EVermicompost%20beds%20have%20been%20created%20to%20support%20the%20health%20of%20the%20soil.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20success%20story%20is%20scripted%20in%20how%20over%2075%2C000%20metric%20tons%20of%20GHG%20(greenhouse%20gas)%20or%20tCO2e%20(metric%20tons%20of%20carbon%20dioxide%20equivalent)%20emissions%20in%20air%20were%20saved%20in%20the%20reporting%20year%20by%20utilising%20agro-residues%20(biogenic%20fuels)%20instead%20of%20coal%20in%20the%20boilers%20of%20the%20manufacturing%20facilities%20at%20the%20Rohad%20and%20Hapur%20plant%20of%20Merino.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMerino%20prides%20itself%20on%20collaborating%20with%20academia%20and%20integrating%20expert%20opinions%20in%20their%20industrial%20processes%2C%20as%20they%20attempt%20to%20align%20with%20sustainable%20goals.%20One%20of%20these%20collaborations%20was%20with%20Visvesvaraya%20National%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20(VNIT%2C%20Nagpur).%20The%20latter%20assisted%20Merino%E2%80%99s%20in-house%20expertise%20in%20assessing%20carbon%20footprint%20and%20accreditation%20as%20per%20ISO%20standards%20and%20also%20pitched%20in%20with%20insights%20on%20developing%20circular%20economy%20principle-based%20projects%20of%20the%20Nirmal%20Program.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20green%20energy%20proposition%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20article%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3EEconomic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20(February%202024)%20highlighted%20a%20report%20by%20India%20Rating%20and%20Research%2C%20noting%20that%20thermal%20power%20represents%2075%20percent%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20total%20power%20generation.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20many%20industries%20use%20thermal%20power%20from%20fossil%20fuels%2C%20we%20are%20among%20the%20first%20to%20experiment%20with%20biomass%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mr%20Lohia%20notes.%20This%20helps%20Merino%20Industries%20promote%20green%20fuel%20and%20support%20local%20communities%20in%20Hapur%20(Uttar%20Pradesh)%20and%20Rohad%20(Haryana)%20by%20ensuring%20consistent%20demand%20for%20agri-residues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-9_11zon-1723195158.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20bamboo%20plantation%20at%20Merino%20Industries%20campus%20enhances%20air%20quality%20in%20the%20area%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-9_11zon-1723195158.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-9_11zon-1723195158-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-9_11zon-1723195158-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-9_11zon-1723195158-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-9_11zon-1723195158-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-360494%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20bamboo%20plantation%20at%20the%20Merino%20Industries%20campus%20enhances%20air%20quality%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-10_11zon-1723195246.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bamboo%20plantations%20are%20a%20key%20feature%20at%20Merino%20Industries%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-10_11zon-1723195246.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-10_11zon-1723195246-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-10_11zon-1723195246-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-10_11zon-1723195246-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-10_11zon-1723195246-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-360496%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EBamboo%20plantations%20are%20a%20key%20feature%20at%20Merino%20Industries.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAside%20from%20achieving%20energy%20efficiency%20using%20green%20fuels%2C%20Lohia%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20have%20turbines%20at%20Hapur%20that%20extract%20energy%20from%20the%20biomass%20furnaces.%20Their%20efficiency%20is%20increased%20following%20some%20retrofitting%20processes.%20A%20similar%20automation%20is%20done%20for%20heating%20and%20cooling%20systems.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%20that%20the%20motors%20at%20Merino%20Industries%20have%20been%20upgraded%20to%20IE3%20technology%2C%20which%20promises%20premium%20efficiency%20while%20being%20environmentally%20friendly.%20Meanwhile%2C%20through%20the%2010.59%20MW%20solar%20power%20system%2C%20approximately%2012.77%20million%20kWh%20units%20of%20electrical%20energy%20are%20generated%20%E2%80%94%20which%20accounts%20for%20around%2024%20percent%20of%20the%20total%20electrical%20energy%20requirement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKey%20features%20of%20Merino%E2%80%99s%20energy%20source%20include%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3Ea)%20Procurement%20from%20the%20local%20community.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3Eb)%20Production%20of%20around%20one%20million%20gigajoules%20of%20energy%20(FY2023-24)%2C%20meeting%20the%20heat%20requirements%20of%20its%20processing%20units%20in%20Hapur%20(Uttar%20Pradesh)%20and%20Rohad%20(Haryana)%20through%20complete%20combustion%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3Ec)%20Reduction%20of%20GHG%20emissions%20by%20approximately%2095%2C000%20MT%20of%20CO2%20equivalent%2C%20which%20would%20have%20otherwise%20been%20generated%20from%20burning%20fossil%20fuels%20like%20coal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3Ed)%20Pioneering%20the%20use%20of%20biomass%20since%202005%20and%20turbine%20technology%20in%20Hapur%20which%20extracts%20energy%20in%20electrical%20form.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-11_11zon-1723195372.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20creation%20of%20Miyawaki%20Forests%20at%20Hapur%20is%20an%20extension%20of%20Merino%20Industries'%20commitment%20to%20sustainability%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-11_11zon-1723195372.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-11_11zon-1723195372-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-11_11zon-1723195372-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-11_11zon-1723195372-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-11_11zon-1723195372-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-360498%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20creation%20of%20Miyawaki%20Forests%20at%20Hapur%20is%20an%20extension%20of%20Merino%20Industries%E2%80%99%20commitment%20to%20sustainability.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20roadmap%20has%20guided%20Merino%20Industries%20in%20achieving%20energy%20efficiency.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20company%20has%20expanded%20its%20focus%20to%20water%2C%20air%2C%20and%20soil%2C%20primarily%20relying%20on%20renewable%20resources%20and%20energy%20sources.%20Merino%20Industries%20is%20pursuing%20a%20%E2%80%98Water%20Neutrality%20Goal%E2%80%99%20through%20efficient%20water%20management%20practices%2C%20striving%20to%20reduce%20emissions%2C%20and%20implementing%20measures%20to%20improve%20air%20quality%20while%20minimising%20greenhouse%20gas%20(GHG)%20emissions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Lohia%20notes%20that%20while%20any%20industry%20would%20attempt%20to%20maximise%20production%20in%20additional%20land%20available%2C%20at%20Merino%2C%20green%20practices%20have%20always%20been%20the%20priority.%20This%20has%20led%20to%20the%20development%20of%20Miyawaki%20forests%20(multi-layered%20forests%20consisting%20of%20native%20plant%20species)%20on%20the%20campus%20at%20Hapur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecognising%20that%20trees%20are%20integral%20for%20clean%20air%2C%20habitat%20preservation%2C%20livelihoods%2C%20watershed%20protection%2C%20soil%20erosion%20prevention%2C%20and%20climate%20change%20mitigation%2C%20Merino%20has%20set%20a%20target%20to%20increase%20green%20cover%20both%20within%20and%20outside%20factory%20premises%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20planting%20of%20over%2020%2C000%20tree%20saplings%20throughout%20India%20during%202023-2024.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20goal%20is%20to%20evolve%20as%20an%20industry%20but%20to%20do%20so%20sustainably.%20By%20blending%20expertise%20and%20resources%2C%20the%20company%20believes%20positive%20transformations%20can%20be%20driven%20in%20society.%20%E2%80%9COur%20strong%20belief%20is%20that%20by%20prioritising%20people%2C%20the%20planet%2C%20and%20sustainable%20product%20offerings%2C%20enterprises%20can%20thrive%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mr%20Lohia%20concludes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723198670000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-1723194040.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D360474%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sustainability%20at%20Merino%20Industries%20is%20viewed%20as%20a%20mindset%20rather%20than%20an%20end%20goal%2C%20driving%20their%20commitment%20to%20eco-friendly%20practices%20and%20renewable%20energy%20alternatives.%20Their%20efforts%20have%20led%20to%2074.6%25%20of%20energy%20needs%20being%20met%20through%20green%20sources.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A283%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F360474%2Fmerino-industries-renewable-green-energy-biomass-husk-solar-power-sustainable-company-practices%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22MBA%20Couple%20Quit%20Corporate%20Life%20to%20%E2%80%98Move%20to%20The%20Hills%E2%80%99%2C%20Start%20Dreamy%20Organic%20Cafe%20in%20Uttarakhand%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20sun%20beat%20down%20on%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Barapullah%20flyover%20in%202017%2C%20a%20couple%20found%20themselves%20caught%20in%20a%20moment%20of%20decisive%20clarity.%20Amit%2C%20an%20employee%20at%20HDFC%20AMC%2C%20confided%20in%20his%20wife%20Shipra%2C%20an%20advertising%20professional%20at%20Outlook%20Magazine%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20can%E2%80%99t%20do%20this%20anymore.%20I%E2%80%99m%20resigning.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20asked%20her%2C%20%E2%80%9CWill%20