and%20despair%20of%20parents%20who%20wish%20to%20get%20justice%20for%20their%20children.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20certain%20cases%2C%20certain%20issues%20like%20this%20which%20really%20shakes%20you%20to%20the%20core.%20When%20you%20see%20people%20almost%20lose%20their%20desire%20to%20live%2C%20it%20really%20weighs%20you%20down.%20What%20keeps%20me%20going%20is%20the%20desire%20to%20get%20them%20justice%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20such%20example%20was%20the%20case%20of%20Aditya%20Prabhu%2C%20a%20young%20boy%20who%20took%20his%20life%20due%20to%20harassment%20from%20college%20authorities.%20Dushyant%20was%20very%20vocal%20about%20getting%20justice%20for%20Aditya%2C%20for%20which%20he%20spent%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20with%20his%20parents%20and%20organised%20protests%20for%20Aditya%20in%20Bengaluru.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC7GxcjiLKRf%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC7GxcjiLKRf%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC7GxcjiLKRf%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20St.%20Broseph%20(%40st_brosephs)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20case%20of%20a%20missing%20doctor%20in%20Ahmedabad%2C%20Dushyant%20personally%20went%20there%20and%20helped%20the%20parents%20file%20a%20case.%20It%20took%208%20months%20of%20relentless%20efforts%20for%20the%20police%20to%20actually%20file%20an%20FIR%2C%20says%20Dushyant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReddit%20is%20filled%20with%20appreciation%20posts%20for%20St%20Broseph%2C%20who%20goes%20above%20and%20beyond%20to%20help%20others%2C%20with%20people%20calling%20him%20Batman%20and%20thanking%20him%20for%20everything%20he%20does.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHitesh%2C%20a%20student%2C%20took%20Dushyant%E2%80%99s%20help%20to%20find%20a%20solution%20for%20a%20pervert%20who%20was%20flashing%20women%20in%20the%20neighbourhood.%20He%20was%20able%20to%20register%20a%20complaint%20and%20the%20case%20is%20in%20court%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBroseph%20helped%20us%20with%20all%20the%20details%20about%20filing%20a%20complaint%20and%20what%20evidence%20is%20needed.%20He%20was%20instrumental%20in%20these%20women%20seeking%20justice.%20His%20team%20followed%20up%20with%20us%20and%20helped%20us%20in%20every%20step.%20We%20have%20our%20own%20Batman%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Hitesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20would%20question%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhat%E2%80%99s%20in%20it%20for%20him%3F%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20have%20the%20right%20to%20work%20but%20never%20to%20its%20fruits.%20Let%20not%20the%20fruits%20of%20action%20be%20your%20motive%2C%20nor%20let%20your%20attachment%20be%20to%20inaction%2C%E2%80%9D%20is%20his%20mantra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20candidly%20accepts%20that%20while%20saying%20it%20is%20easy%2C%20there%20are%20difficult%20days.%20But%20knowing%20that%20this%20is%20the%20right%20path%20helps%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2