22%20Zouhaier%20Sghaier%20Ranking%20Series%20and%20bagging%20her%20first%20senior%20gold%20medal%20in%20July.%20The%20Indian%20wrestler%20defeated%20USA%E2%80%99s%20Dominique%20Parrish%2C%20who%20became%20the%20world%20champion%20in%20the%20category%20a%20couple%20of%20months%20later%2C%20en%20route%20to%20the%20title%20in%20Tunis.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20months%20later%2C%20Antim%20would%20go%20on%20to%20win%20a%20historic%20gold%20medal%20at%20the%20U-20%20World%20Wrestling%20Championships%202022%20in%20Sofia%2C%20Bulgaria%2C%20becoming%20the%20first%20Indian%20to%20win%20the%20title%20in%20the%20competition%E2%80%99s%20history.%20A%20year%20later%2C%20she%20successfully%20defended%20her%20crown%20in%20Amman%2C%20becoming%20the%20only%20two-time%20junior%20world%20champion%20from%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20April%202023%2C%20Antim%20won%20a%20silver%20medal%20at%20the%20Asian%20Championships%20in%20Astana.%20It%20took%20Japan%E2%80%99s%20Akari%20Fujinami%2C%20a%20true%20modern-day%20wrestling%20phenom%20who%20is%20yet%20to%20lose%20a%20senior%20bout%20in%20her%20career%2C%20to%20end%20Antim%E2%80%99s%20run%20in%20the%20final%20at%20Astana.%20Having%20missed%20out%20on%20the%20world%20championships%20in%202022%20due%20to%20Vinesh%20Phogat%E2%80%99s%20presence%2C%20Antim%20finally%20made%20her%20debut%20at%20the%20global%20meet%20in%202023%20and%20secured%20a%20bronze%20medal%20from%20Belgrade.%C2%A0Antim%20upset%20defending%20champion%20Parrish%20in%20the%20opening%20round%20but%20fell%20to%20Vanesa%20Kaladzinskaya%20of%20Belarus%20in%20the%20semis.%20She%20secured%20her%20bronze%20with%20a%20commanding%20win%20over%20Sweden%E2%80%99s%20Jonna%20Malmgren%2C%20a%20two-time%20European%20champion.%20Courtesy%20of%20this%20win%2C%20Antim%20also%20secured%20a%20Paris%202024%20Olympic%20quota%20for%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC9Oly5qq0lA